NK047(tsi)006:10702: bdag tu 'dzin pa yin pas de khegs na las
NK047(tsi)006:10703: nyon gyis srid par skye ba khegs shing /
NK047(tsi)006:10704: lam gang gis khegs na gang zag de stong par shes pas 'gog dgos la /
NK047(tsi)006:10707: dmigs yul gyi phung po la brten nas btags pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:10708: nga tsam ngar 'dzin lhan skyes kyi yul du gyur
NK047(tsi)006:10709: pa de brten nas btags pa'am /
NK047(tsi)006:10711: rkyen nyid 'di pa tsam las rang gi ngo bos grub pa cung zad kyang med par shes pas /
NK047(tsi)006:10712: thag pa la sbrul 'dzin ldog pa bzhin du bdag 'dzin ldog ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10713: rdul dang skad cig du ma'i cha ni bdag 'dzin
NK047(tsi)006:10714: lhan skyes kyi 'dzin stangs kyi zhen yul dang dngos
NK047(tsi)006:10715: su 'gal bas de rnams bdag gis stong pa yin
NK047(tsi)006:10716: par shes shing goms pas bdag 'dzin rtsa ba nas
NK047(tsi)006:10717: ldog la / des nyon mongs pa rnams kyang ldog
NK047(tsi)006:10718: pa de tsam gyis 'khor ba las thar bar mthong
NK047(tsi)006:10719: nas theg dman pa dag gzhan chos thams cad la
NK047(tsi)006:10720: bdag med don du mi gnyer mi bsgom pa des
NK047(tsi)006:10721: na mngon du gyur pa'ang med la /
NK047(tsi)006:10722: de med pas spang bya shes sgrib spangs pa'ang med do //
NK047(tsi)006:10723: des na ji srid rang rgyud kyi phung po rgyun
NK047(tsi)006:10724: dang tshogs pa blos ma phye ba tsam la nga
NK047(tsi)006:10726: phung po de dag du mar bsil zhing blos shigs par ma gyur pa zhig na /
NK047(tsi)006:10727: gang zag gi bdag med kyang rtogs thabs med de /
NK047(tsi)006:10728: bdag tu gdags pa'i rgyu phung po la dmigs pas na /
NK047(tsi)006:10730: nyan thos kyi dbang du byas nas phung po ni
NK047(tsi)006:10731: du ma 'dus pa'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir don
NK047(tsi)006:10732: dam par don du med tshul gyi rigs pa gsungs
NK047(tsi)006:10733: te / nyan thos la bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK047(tsi)006:10734: gzugs ni lbu ba rdos pa 'dra //
NK047(tsi)006:10735: zhes pa la sogs pa'i don bzhin phung po nyid
NK047(tsi)006:10736: du ma'i cha la btags pa'i tshul rtogs pa des
NK047(tsi)006:10737: gang zag gi bdag med pa yongs su rdzogs par
NK047(tsi)006:10739: bdag med 'di ni 'gro ba rnams grol phyir //
NK047(tsi)006:10741: de la gang zag gi bdag med ni nyan thos rnams grol ba'i phyir bstan la /
NK047(tsi)006:10742: byang sems rnams thams cad mkhyen pa 'thob pa'i phyir gnyis ka bstan to //
NK047(tsi)006:10743: nyan rang gis kyang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba rkyen nyid 'di pa tsam mthong mod kyi /
NK047(tsi)006:10744: de lta na'ang de dag la chos kyi bdag med pa yongs su rdzogs par sgom pa med de /
NK047(tsi)006:10745: khams gsum na spyod pa'i nyon mongs spong ba'i thabs tsam zhig ni yod do //
NK047(tsi)006:10746: de dag la gang zag gi bdag med pa ma
NK047(tsi)006:10747: lus par sgom pa ni yod par rnam par bzhag
NK047(tsi)006:10748: go // zhes gsungs pa'i lung 'dis nyan rang la
NK047(tsi)006:10749: chos bdag med rdzogs par rtogs pa med pa'ang nges
NK047(tsi)006:10750: go // nus te / chos bdag med rdzogs par rtogs pa min tshe nyon mongs mi spong na /
NK047(tsi)006:10751: nyan thos kyis kyang de rdzogs par ma bsgoms na nyon mongs ga la spong ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10753: rigs pa'ang gang zag gi bdag med pa tsam kho
NK047(tsi)006:10754: nas nyon mongs spong tshul rnam 'grel dang rigs tshogs
NK047(tsi)006:10755: kyis bstan pa ltar rgya che zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10756: chos bdag med ma rdzogs na'ang de rtogs pa yod
NK047(tsi)006:10757: par rnam bdun shing rta'i rigs pa sogs kyis grub
NK047(tsi)006:10758: cing / de goms pas gsal snang rab kyang 'byung bar grub bo //
NK047(tsi)006:10759: de'ang tshogs mtha' yas pa sogs mdor na thabs khyad
NK047(tsi)006:10760: par can gyi rgyu ma tshang na rtogs pa khyad
NK047(tsi)006:10761: par can mi skye bar nges shing /
NK047(tsi)006:10762: gang du rgyu tshang ba la sa dang po'i ye shes sogs rtogs pa khyad par can skye zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10763: de skyes pa'i tshe de'i ngos skal gyi spang bya'ang med par shes par bya la /
NK047(tsi)006:10764: spang bya dang bral na de'i ngos skal gyi yon tan kyang rdzogs pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10765: de gsum rnam pa kun tu rjes su 'gro ldog mtshungs pa yin nges kyi /
NK047(tsi)006:10766: de ltar min na de'i nang gi gang rung yod
NK047(tsi)006:10767: la gang rung med pa sogs mu ji snyed pa
NK047(tsi)006:10769: de ltar na spang bya thams cad spangs la rtogs
NK047(tsi)006:10770: bya mtha' dag ma rtogs pa sogs mu rnams so
NK047(tsi)006:10771: so nas srid par smra ba'i rgol ba la /
NK047(tsi)006:10772: dngos stobs kyi rigs pa'i lam nas dgag pa yang
NK047(tsi)006:10773: dag bstan du med par 'gyur bas na de ltar
NK047(tsi)006:10775: mdor na nyan rang la chos bdag med rdzogs par
NK047(tsi)006:10776: rtogs pa yod na bka' dang dgongs 'grel mtha' dag
NK047(tsi)006:10777: gi lung dang / rigs pa brgya phrag gis gnod pa 'da' dka' zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10778: theg pa che chung gi mthong lam sogs lam dang
NK047(tsi)006:10779: 'bras bu'i yon tan ni nyi ma dang me khyer
NK047(tsi)006:10780: la gsal mi gsal gyi khyad bzhin du mchis na
NK047(tsi)006:10781: / de dag gang la brten pa rtogs pa ye
NK047(tsi)006:10782: shes 'od lta bu la khyad zhugs pa shes par
NK047(tsi)006:10783: / bya'o // de ltar rigs pa'i gnad tsam bstan pas blo ldan rnams la chog gi /
NK047(tsi)006:10785: spyir 'di rigs skor theg gsum lam gyi 'gros che ba yin cing /
NK047(tsi)006:10786: tshul de la shing rta chen po gnyis la sogs
NK047(tsi)006:10787: pa'i dgongs pa 'gal ba lta bur 'dzin dgos na
NK047(tsi)006:10788: yid la zug rngu ltar mchi zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10789: gang ci la'ang shing rta chen po rnams kyi dgongs
NK047(tsi)006:10790: pa'i gnad 'bras chan la mngar gsum gyi phye btab
NK047(tsi)006:10791: pa bzhin lhan cig yi gas bde bar 'ju ba
NK047(tsi)006:10792: byung zhing / gzhan la zer 'dod kyi 'gram chu mi ldang la /
NK047(tsi)006:10793: gzhan mthong gi yid smon yang mi dgos par /
NK047(tsi)006:10794: rang mal na rang blo bde ba zhig byung na
NK047(tsi)006:10795: thos bsam pa dag la rnyed pa'i mchog zhig ste
NK047(tsi)006:10796: / gzhan dag su ma mgu yang zhe blo bde /
NK047(tsi)006:10799: mkhan slob chos gsum gyi rjes 'jug snga 'gyur pa rnams /
NK047(tsi)006:10800: rgyal ba'i bka' dri med dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10801: rgyan drug rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa'i gzhung bzang po snga 'gyur 'di tsam gda' bas /
NK047(tsi)006:10802: thos bsam de la byas pas chog gi /
NK047(tsi)006:10803: gzhan zer rjes brjod la dga' ba tsam gyis ci bya ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10804: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha dang dam pa'i gzhung
NK047(tsi)006:10805: gi snang ba dang rtag tu 'grogs par mdzod cig
NK047(tsi)006:10806: / gnyis pa kun rdzob don byed nus snang du khas blangs pa'i phan yon /
NK047(tsi)006:10807: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i dngos po ni //
NK047(tsi)006:10808: kun rdzob tu ni ma bzlog pas //
NK047(tsi)006:10809: kun nas nyon mongs rnam byang sogs //
NK047(tsi)006:10810: rnam par gzhag pa 'khrugs pa med //
NK047(tsi)006:10812: de la dngos smra ba rnams na re /
NK047(tsi)006:10814: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10815: rnam par byang ba'i khyad par dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10816: de bzhin du dge mi dge /
NK047(tsi)006:10818: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba lugs 'byung ldog /
NK047(tsi)006:10819: rjes su dpags bya dang dpogs byed dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10820: rtags las rtags can gyi blo 'byung ba lta bu
NK047(tsi)006:10821: bskyed bya skyed byed sogs shes bya rgyu 'bras so
NK047(tsi)006:10822: so'i mtshan nyid ma 'dres par gzhag tu mi rung
NK047(tsi)006:10823: ngo snyam pa la sogs pa'i klan ka ngan pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:10824: yid dang smra ba thams cad bsal nas rgyu 'bras
NK047(tsi)006:10825: 'thad par bstan pa'i tshigs su bcad pa 'di gsungs
NK047(tsi)006:10826: so // de'ang skyed byed rgyu dang bskyed bya 'brasa
NK047(tsi)006:10827: bu'i dngosa po don byed nus kyi snang ba 'gog
NK047(tsi)006:10828: so // med 'di ni / kuna rdzoba tsam du
NK047(tsi)006:10829: yod pa ni ma bzloga par tha snyad kyi tshad
NK047(tsi)006:10830: mas de ltar gzhal nas 'jog pa yin pasa na
NK047(tsi)006:10831: so // med 'di ni / / kuna nasa nyon
NK047(tsi)006:10832: mongas pa dang rnama par byang ba sogas kyi rgyu
NK047(tsi)006:10833: 'bras rjes su 'gro ldog gi tshul rnama para gazhaga
NK047(tsi)006:10834: pa kun so so rang gi mtshan nyid ma nyams
NK047(tsi)006:10835: par gnas kyi rang bzhin med par bstan pas kun
NK047(tsi)006:10836: rdzob kyi mtshan nyid de dag 'khrugsa shing 'chol bar
NK047(tsi)006:10837: gyur pa ni cung zad kyang meda do zhes so
NK047(tsi)006:10839: dngos po rnams kyi mtshan nyid gra ma nyams par
NK047(tsi)006:10840: 'jog nus na kho bo cag dang 'dod pa gcig
NK047(tsi)006:10842: khyed cag 'di ltar snang ba ltar don dam par grub par 'dod pas /
NK047(tsi)006:10843: de ltar na rdul phra rab nas rnam par shes
NK047(tsi)006:10844: pa la thug gi bar gcig pa'am du ma'i rang
NK047(tsi)006:10846: sngar brjod pa rnams kyi lan thobs shig dang de tshe rigs pas gnod med du 'grub nus na /
NK047(tsi)006:10847: kho bo cag dang khyod mthun par 'gyur te /
NK047(tsi)006:10848: dngos po 'di dag don dam par yang brdzun pa ma yin pa mi bslu ba'i chos can no //
NK047(tsi)006:10849: zhes bdag cag kyang khas len to //
NK047(tsi)006:10851: kho bo cag gis ji skad bstan pa'i rigs pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:10852: rjes su zhugs la 'di snang yang brdzun par khas
NK047(tsi)006:10853: longs dang 'u bu cag mthun no //
NK047(tsi)006:10854: gzhan du ji ltar don gcig pa yin zhes smra bar nus pa ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10855: de ltar rang bzhin stong pa la nges pa rnal
NK047(tsi)006:10856: ma zhig 'drongs na rgyu dang 'bras bu la yid
NK047(tsi)006:10857: ches mi ldog pa zhig skye nges pa yin no
NK047(tsi)006:10858: // de ltar ma yin par rgyu dang 'bras bu mi 'thad pa 'dra ba'i tshul du go na /
NK047(tsi)006:10859: de dbu ma nas bshad pa'i stong pa nyid ni ma yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:10860: chad lta la stong pa'i ming gis btags pa'i lam yin par shes nas ring du spang bar bya'o //
NK047(tsi)006:10861: ji skad du slob dpon klus /
NK047(tsi)006:10862: rnam par dben don mi shes la //
NK047(tsi)006:10863: thos pa tsam la 'jug byed cing //
NK047(tsi)006:10864: gang dag bsod nams mi byed pa //
NK047(tsi)006:10865: skyes bu tha shal de dag brlag /
NK047(tsi)006:10866: las kyi 'bras bu yod pa dang //
NK047(tsi)006:10867: 'gro ba dag kyang shin tu brjod //
NK047(tsi)006:10868: de yi rang bzhin yongs shes dang //
NK047(tsi)006:10869: skye ba med pa dag kyang bstan //
NK047(tsi)006:10870: 'jig rten dbang du rgyal ba rnams //
NK047(tsi)006:10871: nga dang nga yi zhes gsungs ltar //
NK047(tsi)006:10872: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK047(tsi)006:10873: de bzhin dgongs pa'i dbang gis gsungs //
NK047(tsi)006:10875: gzhan yang stong pa nyid shin tu zab pas blta dka' zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10876: blo gros chung ba rnams go ba phyin ci log
NK047(tsi)006:10877: tu gyur na phung bar 'gyur ba'i tshul mang du
NK047(tsi)006:10880: tshogs rnam dag 'byung bar mdor bstan //
NK047(tsi)006:10881: de'i tshul rgyas par bshad pa gnyis //
NK047(tsi)006:10884: chos 'di rnam par bzhag pas na //
NK047(tsi)006:10885: tshogs rnams dri ma med pa yang //
NK047(tsi)006:10886: gzhung 'di nyid la rung ba yin //
NK047(tsi)006:10888: 'di ltar rang bzhin med pa'i tshul gyi rgyu dang 'brasa bu yi /
NK047(tsi)006:10889: chosa 'di rnam para bazhaga pasa na /
NK047(tsi)006:10890: sbyin sogs bsod nams kyi tshogas rnamas kyang kun rmongs
NK047(tsi)006:10891: kyi dri ma meda pa'i ye shes kyi tshogs dang
NK047(tsi)006:10892: zung du 'brel ba'i lam rnam par dag pa yanga
NK047(tsi)006:10893: / gzhunga 'di lta bu nyid la runga ba yina gyi /
NK047(tsi)006:10894: gzhan dngos por smra ba sogs la ni ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10895: de'ang don dam par rang bzhin med kyang kun rdzob
NK047(tsi)006:10896: snang cha'i rten 'brel bslu ba med pa'i yin tshul
NK047(tsi)006:10897: shes nas lam la slob pa ni dngos po'i gnas
NK047(tsi)006:10898: lugs la phyin ci log gis blo bslad pa med
NK047(tsi)006:10899: pas na rnam par dag pa nyid du 'gyur ba
NK047(tsi)006:10900: yin no // de la dmigs pa can rnams na re /
NK047(tsi)006:10901: sbyin pa gang zhig phan gdags dang //
NK047(tsi)006:10902: mchod pa'i phyir yang sbyin byed pa //
NK047(tsi)006:10903: de ni shin tu dad par byed //
NK047(tsi)006:10904: mthong med gnas pas ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10905: med pa'i phyir ni mi dmigs sam //
NK047(tsi)006:10906: 'on te yul min phyir ram ci //
NK047(tsi)006:10908: ngal ba'i don yang med par 'gyur //
NK047(tsi)006:10909: gsum char rgyal bas gzigs pas na //
NK047(tsi)006:10910: de bas yul min ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10911: rang gi sems dang sems byung gang //
NK047(tsi)006:10912: de dag rang gis rig par byed //
NK047(tsi)006:10913: ces sbyin pa ni phan 'dogs pa'am mchod pa'i sems
NK047(tsi)006:10914: kyis yul dmigs nas sbyin pa ni shin du dwang
NK047(tsi)006:10915: ba bskyed kyi / yul ma dmigs pas ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10916: de la yul med nas ma dmigs na ni byang
NK047(tsi)006:10917: sems rnams sems can gyi don du ngal ba'ang don
NK047(tsi)006:10918: med de sems can rnams med pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:10919: yul ma yin pa'ang min te /
NK047(tsi)006:10920: sbyin po sbyin bya len po gsum char de bzhin gshegs pas gzigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:10921: gzhan yang sbyin bya bu la sogs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10922: len po dang gtong po dag gi rang gi sems
NK047(tsi)006:10923: dang sems byung dag rang gis rig par byed na
NK047(tsi)006:10924: de ji ltar yul min zhes rgol ba de dag
NK047(tsi)006:10925: la snying po ci'ang med de /
NK047(tsi)006:10926: kun rdzob tu rgyu 'bras kyi rten 'brel med ces dgag pa ma yin na /
NK047(tsi)006:10927: gsum char rgyal bas gzigs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10928: rang rig ces pa'ang kun rdzob tu yin gyi /
NK047(tsi)006:10929: don dam par gcig dang du ma'i rang bzhin dang bral bas de dag ga la yod do //
NK047(tsi)006:10931: rgyu 'bras rjes su 'gro ldog yin pa'i dpe spyir bstan pa /
NK047(tsi)006:10932: lta ba rnam dag gis zin ma zin gyi rgyu 'bras bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)006:10934: rnam par dag pa'i rgyu las ni //
NK047(tsi)006:10936: yang dag ltas byung tshul khrims kyi //
NK047(tsi)006:10937: yan lag la sogs rnam dag bzhin //
NK047(tsi)006:10938: de bzhin rnam dag ma yin las //
NK047(tsi)006:10940: log lta'i stobs las byung ba yi //
NK047(tsi)006:10941: log par g.yems la sogs pa bzhin //
NK047(tsi)006:10943: 'bras bu thams cad ni rgyu'i rjes su 'gro ba dang /
NK047(tsi)006:10946: rgyu rnam par dag ma dag gi 'bras bu'ang rnam par dag ma dag tu 'gyur ba yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:10947: de'ang rnama para daga pa'i rgyu lasa ni /
NK047(tsi)006:10948: 'brasa bu'ang rnam para daga pa 'byung ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10949: dper na legs par spyad pa dang nyes par spyad
NK047(tsi)006:10950: pa'i las rnams kyi 'bras bu yod par lta ba
NK047(tsi)006:10951: 'jig rten pa'i yang dag par lta ba las byung
NK047(tsi)006:10952: ba'i srog mi gcod pa sogs tshul khrimas kyi yan
NK047(tsi)006:10953: lag dang / de bzhin du bag yod kyi yan
NK047(tsi)006:10954: lag la sogas pa'ang rnam par daga pa nyid du
NK047(tsi)006:10956: rgyu lta bu'i rjes su 'bras bu tshul khrims kyi
NK047(tsi)006:10957: yan lag sogs kyang 'brangs nas rnam par dag pa
NK047(tsi)006:10958: de bzhina du / gal te rgyu rnam daga ma yina pa zhig na de lasa /
NK047(tsi)006:10959: 'brasa bu dag kyang rnama daga ma yina pa 'byunga ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10960: dper na las 'bras med par lta ba loga lta'i
NK047(tsi)006:10961: stobsa las byung ba yi loga para g.yemas pa la
NK047(tsi)006:10962: sogsa pa'i mi dge ba spyod pa bzhina no //
NK047(tsi)006:10964: tshad ma'i gnod pa yod pas na //
NK047(tsi)006:10965: dngos por dmigs pa yod pa ni //
NK047(tsi)006:10966: smig rgyu la sogs shes pa bzhin //
NK047(tsi)006:10967: phyin ci log par yongs su rtog /
NK047(tsi)006:10968: de phyir de mthus byung ba yi //
NK047(tsi)006:10969: pha rol phyin pa sgrub pa kun //
NK047(tsi)006:10970: bdag dang bdag gir log pa las //
NK047(tsi)006:10971: byung ba bzhin du stobs chung ngo //
NK047(tsi)006:10972: dngos por dmigs pa med pa las //
NK047(tsi)006:10973: byung ba 'bras bu chen po ste //
NK047(tsi)006:10974: rgyas pa'i rgyu las byung ba'i phyir //
NK047(tsi)006:10975: sa bon grung po'i myug sogs bzhin //
NK047(tsi)006:10977: gong du 'bras bu rnam par dag mi dag rgyu la rag las pa'i tshul spyir bstan nas /
NK047(tsi)006:10978: skabs su babs pa dngos por dmigs pa can gyi sbyin sogs tshogs rnam dag ma yin zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:10979: dngos por dmigs pa med pa'i sbyin sogs la spyad pa tshogs rnam dag yin par ston la /
NK047(tsi)006:10980: de'ang ci'i phyir dngos por dmigs pas tshogs mi dag snyam na /
NK047(tsi)006:10981: 'di ltar yang dag pa'i rigs pas dpyad na /
NK047(tsi)006:10982: tshad ma'i gnoda pa yoda pasa na dngos por yod pa ma yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:10983: dngos po med bzhin du dngosa pora dmigas pa yoda pa can ni /
NK047(tsi)006:10984: phyin ci log gi rtog pas bslad pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:10985: dper na smiga rgyu la chur shes pa dang mgal
NK047(tsi)006:10986: me la 'khor lor 'dzin pa la sogas pa'i shesa
NK047(tsi)006:10987: pa bzhina du yul gyi gnas tshul phyin ci loga
NK047(tsi)006:10988: para yongas su rtog pa yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:10989: de ltar dngos por 'dzin pa log shes yin pa de yi phyir na /
NK047(tsi)006:10990: dngos 'dzin gyi lta ba de yi mthu las byung
NK047(tsi)006:10991: ba yi sbyin sogs pha rola phyin pa sgrub pa
NK047(tsi)006:10992: kun kyang dngos po'i rang bzhin la sgrib par byed
NK047(tsi)006:10993: pa phyin ci log gi rtog pas bslad pas /
NK047(tsi)006:10994: dper na mu stegs rnams kyis bdag med pa la
NK047(tsi)006:10995: badga dang badga gira bzung ste loga par zhen pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:10996: 'jig tshogs lta ba la gnas bzhin pa lasa byung
NK047(tsi)006:10997: ba'i dka' thub la sogs pa rdzogs byang gi yan
NK047(tsi)006:10998: lag yang dag pa'i lam du mi rung ba bzhina
NK047(tsi)006:10999: du / dngos zhen can gyis lam bsgrubs pa 'adi'ang
NK047(tsi)006:11000: nor ba'i blo yi dbang du song nas stobsa chung
NK047(tsi)006:11001: du / ngo // de las bzlog ste dngosa pora
NK047(tsi)006:11002: dmigas pa meda pa lasa byung ba sbyin sogs ni
NK047(tsi)006:11003: mthar thug gi 'brasa bu chena po sangs rgyas nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11005: dngos po'i yin tshul ma nor ba'i ye shes kyi dbang du byas pas na /
NK047(tsi)006:11007: rgyas par byed pa'i rgyu rnam dag lasa byung ba'i phyir /
NK047(tsi)006:11008: dper na sa bona grunga po sta /
NK047(tsi)006:11009: skyon ma zhugs pa'i myu gu dang snye ma la sogas pa bzhina no //
NK047(tsi)006:11011: de la bdag tu dmigs bzhin du rdzogs byang don
NK047(tsi)006:11012: gnyer gyi dge ba rnams kyang rnam mkhyen gyi rgyur
NK047(tsi)006:11014: brgyud nas 'gyur ba tsam yin gyi dngos su ni ma yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11015: dngos su bdag lta dang ma bral bzhin du thar lam rnal ma mi 'byung ba yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11016: de mi 'byung ba'i gnad kyang phyin ci log gi lta bas bslad pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11018: de ma thag tu yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK047(tsi)006:11019: chub kyi yan lag tu mi 'gyur zhes de ma
NK047(tsi)006:11020: thag pa'i don bar du gzhan brgyud dgos pa'i don
NK047(tsi)006:11021: to // des na mchod dang phan gdags par 'dod
NK047(tsi)006:11022: pas gang sbyin pa de'ang 'khor gsum dag par byin
NK047(tsi)006:11023: na de nyid blo gros dang ldan pa rnams kyis
NK047(tsi)006:11024: yi rang ba'i gnas su 'gyur te /
NK047(tsi)006:11025: phyin ci ma log par shes shing tshul bzhin zhugs
NK047(tsi)006:11026: pa gti mug med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba yin
NK047(tsi)006:11028: chos yang dag par sdud pa las /
NK047(tsi)006:11029: bcom ldan 'das chos thams cad mi mthong ba ni yang dag par mthong ba'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11031: rgyal ba'i yum sum brgya pa las /
NK047(tsi)006:11033: shar phyogs kyi nam mkha' tshad gzung bar sla'am /
NK047(tsi)006:11035: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma lags so //
NK047(tsi)006:11037: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' gang
NK047(tsi)006:11038: mi gnas par yongs su mi gnas par sbyin pa
NK047(tsi)006:11039: gtong ba de'i bsod nams kyi phung po'ang tshad gzung
NK047(tsi)006:11040: bar sla ba ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11041: zhes bya ba'i bar du gsungs so //
NK047(tsi)006:11044: dper na mig dang ldan pa'i mi zhig mun par
NK047(tsi)006:11045: zhugs na ci'ang mi mthong ba de bzhin du gang
NK047(tsi)006:11046: dngos por ltungs pa'i sbyin pa yongs su gtong ba'i
NK047(tsi)006:11049: dper na nam langs te nyi ma shar nas mig
NK047(tsi)006:11050: dang ldan pa'i mis gzugs rnam pa sna tshogs dag
NK047(tsi)006:11051: mthong ba de bzhin du gang dngos por ma lhungs
NK047(tsi)006:11052: pas sbyin pa yongs su gtong ba'i byang chub sems
NK047(tsi)006:11054: gnyis pa bden gnyis de 'dra ba'i tshul la basngagasa pa'i don bsdu ba la /
NK047(tsi)006:11055: tshul gnyis shing rta'i srol rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11057: dang po la tha snyad kyi de kho na nyid rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11058: tshul gnyis zung du 'brel ba'i lam rnam par gzhag pa gnyis /
NK047(tsi)006:11060: rgyu dang 'bras bur gyur pa yang //
NK047(tsi)006:11061: shes pa 'ba' zhig kho na ste //
NK047(tsi)006:11062: rang gis grub pa gang yin pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11063: de ni shes par gnas pa yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11065: 'o na de ltar rgyu dang 'bras bur gyur pa
NK047(tsi)006:11066: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i snang tshul de dag
NK047(tsi)006:11067: sems dang sems byung tsam gyi bdag nyid kho na'am
NK047(tsi)006:11068: / ci ste phyi'i bdag nyid yin zhe na //
NK047(tsi)006:11069: de la slob dpon legs ldan byed la sogs pa ni phyi'i bdag nyid du bzhed de /
NK047(tsi)006:11070: mdo las sems tsam zhes gsungs pa byed pa po dang za ba po dgag pa'i ched yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11072: de las gzhan pa gzhung 'dir ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11073: rgyu dang 'brasa bura gyur pa yanga /
NK047(tsi)006:11074: shesa pa 'ab'a zhiga kho na ma gtogs phyi rol gyi don gud na med par 'dod pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11075: shes pa ranga gisa gsal por nyams su myongs pas
NK047(tsi)006:11076: gruba pa ganga yina pa de ni shesa para gansa
NK047(tsi)006:11077: pa yina gyi gzhan du mi 'thad do //
NK047(tsi)006:11078: de la gang snang zhing shes pa de dag shes
NK047(tsi)006:11079: pa rang gis myong ba dang tha mi dad kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11080: / rang gis gsal por myongs bas grub pa'i ngo bo de spangs nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11081: don gzhan de nyid rtog pa'i tshul nam yang mi srid de /
NK047(tsi)006:11082: gal te srid na gsal rig dang bral bzhin rtog dgos la /
NK047(tsi)006:11083: gsal rig dang bral na shes pa nyid du mi rung zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11084: de lta bas na shes pa ni med la don gsal ba ni yod pa zhig mi rung bas /
NK047(tsi)006:11085: gang myong ba thams cad shes pa nyid yin par grub ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11086: rmi lam dang sgyu ma la sogs pa'i gzugs bzhin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11087: gal te gzugs la sogs pa'i phyi rol gyi don
NK047(tsi)006:11088: rnams rnam shes las gud du yod par chug na'ang
NK047(tsi)006:11089: / mig la sogs pa bzhin du dus mnyam pa
NK047(tsi)006:11090: dang mi mnyam pa'i tshe na'ang 'brel ba'i rgyu med
NK047(tsi)006:11091: pas mngon sum gyis grub par mi 'gyur ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11092: de bas na sngo sogs myong ba ni shes pa
NK047(tsi)006:11093: dang tha dad ma yin pa'i ngo bo myong ste
NK047(tsi)006:11094: / rmi lam la sogs pa'i gzugs myong ba bzhin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11095: gal te rnam pa myong ba ni shes pa yin dgos kyang /
NK047(tsi)006:11096: rnam pa de gtod byed kyi phyi don yod dgos par rjes su dpags so snyam na /
NK047(tsi)006:11097: de ltar na phyi don rdul phra mo la sogs
NK047(tsi)006:11098: pa med par yang rjes su dpags pa'i phyir de
NK047(tsi)006:11100: yod par dpags pa'i lugs la'ang mngon sum du ni
NK047(tsi)006:11101: mi 'grub pa'i lkog gyur la rjes dpags tsam yin
NK047(tsi)006:11102: la / phyi don med pa'i rjes dpags dang mngon
NK047(tsi)006:11103: sum myong ba sems rang gis grub pa tsam ni
NK047(tsi)006:11104: shin tu stobs dang ldan pas phyogs gzhan gyis 'phrog
NK047(tsi)006:11106: de ltar byas na rgyan stug po bkod pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11108: lang kar gshegs pa la sogs pa'i mdo rnams dang yang mthun pa yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11109: des na rjes thob shan 'byed pa'i tshe dbu ma
NK047(tsi)006:11110: pa la tha snyad du phyi don 'dod pa dang
NK047(tsi)006:11111: mi 'dod pa gnyis las mtha' gzhan sel ba yin
NK047(tsi)006:11113: sems tsam la ni brten nas su //
NK047(tsi)006:11114: phyi rol dngos med shes par bya //
NK047(tsi)006:11115: tshul 'dir brten nas de la yang //
NK047(tsi)006:11116: shin tu bdag med shes par bya //
NK047(tsi)006:11118: snang tshod pa 'di kun semas tsam las phyi rol
NK047(tsi)006:11119: don du med par shes pa'i tshul la ni brten
NK047(tsi)006:11120: nas su / phyi rola gyi don dngosa meda du shesa para bya zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11121: de nas tshula 'dira ji skad bshad pa'i gcig dang
NK047(tsi)006:11122: du mar bral ba'i gtan tshigs la brtena nasa sems
NK047(tsi)006:11123: de la yanga / shin tu badga meda pa mtha'
NK047(tsi)006:11124: thams cad spangs pa spros bral dbu ma'i tshul nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11126: de ltar na 'jig rten las 'das pa'i le'u las /
NK047(tsi)006:11128: rgyal ba'i sras khams gsum po ni sems tsam du rtogs te /
NK047(tsi)006:11129: dus gsum yang sems dang mtshungs par rtogs so //
NK047(tsi)006:11130: sems de'ang mtha' dang dbus med par khong du chud do //
NK047(tsi)006:11131: zhes bstan pa 'di legs par bshad par 'gyur te /
NK047(tsi)006:11132: phyogs dus kyi snang ba thams cad sems su shes shing /
NK047(tsi)006:11133: sems de'ang skye ba dang 'jig pa'i mtha' dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11134: da lta gnas pa'i mtshan nyid dbus med par mtha' bral du shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11135: chos yang dag par sdud pa las kyang /
NK047(tsi)006:11136: bcom ldan 'das chos thams cad ni kun brtags pa'i snying po ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11139: sgyu ma lta bu rtsa ba ma mchis pa'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11141: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa las /
NK047(tsi)006:11142: 'di ltar sems de ni sems ma mchis pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11143: sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'od gsal ba lags so //
NK047(tsi)006:11145: gnyis pa de la basngagasa pa la /
NK047(tsi)006:11148: tshul gnyis shing rta zhon nas su //
NK047(tsi)006:11149: rigs pa'i srab skyogs 'ju byed pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11150: de dag de phyir ji bzhin don //
NK047(tsi)006:11151: theg pa chen po pa nyid 'thob //
NK047(tsi)006:11153: de ltar tha snyad sems tsam gyi tshul dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11154: don dam dbu ma'i tshul te /
NK047(tsi)006:11155: tshula de gnyis zung du 'brel ba'i lam shinga rta chen po la zhona nasa su /
NK047(tsi)006:11156: bden gnyis dpyod pa'i tshad ma shes rab dri med
NK047(tsi)006:11157: kyi rigas pa'i sraba skyogsa mi gtong bar 'ju bar
NK047(tsi)006:11159: rmad du byung ba'i tshul bzang po la gnas pa de nyid kyi phyir /
NK047(tsi)006:11160: ji bzhiina dona dang ldan pa'i thega pa chen po pa zhes pa'i ming nyid 'thoba pa yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11161: de la sangs rgyas kyi theg pa chen po ni gnyis te /
NK047(tsi)006:11162: zab pa dang rgya che ba'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11163: de dag ston par byed pa'ang dbu sems kyi gzhung lugs ston par byed pa'i bka' rnams so //
NK047(tsi)006:11164: de dag gi dgongs pa 'grel pa'ang klu sgrub dang
NK047(tsi)006:11165: thogs med de shing rta rnam pa gnyis kyi lam
NK047(tsi)006:11167: lam de dag kyang rang rang gis gang 'dod pa
NK047(tsi)006:11168: nyid rtsal du bton te phyogs bcad pa lta bu
NK047(tsi)006:11170: sangs rgyas kyi bka' zab mo'i cha dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11171: rgya che ba'i cha gnyis gsal bar byas pa tsam mo //
NK047(tsi)006:11172: des na de dag gi dgongs pa zung gcig tu chud na /
NK047(tsi)006:11173: bcom ldan 'das kyis tha snyad kun rdzob bden pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11174: rnam gzhag kun nyon dang rnam byang gis bsdus pa
NK047(tsi)006:11175: ji snyed bka' stsal pa'i mthar thug pa sems tsam
NK047(tsi)006:11176: gyi tshul rtogs pa la rag las shing /
NK047(tsi)006:11177: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar gyi chos thams cad rang
NK047(tsi)006:11178: bzhin spros bral chen por gtan la 'bebs pa mthar
NK047(tsi)006:11179: thug dbu ma la thug pa'i phyir na /
NK047(tsi)006:11180: zab pa dang rgya che ba'i phyogs ris su chad
NK047(tsi)006:11181: pa med pa'i theg pa chen po la zhugs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11182: yin no // des na tshul gnyis shing rta chen
NK047(tsi)006:11183: po'i gzhung mkha' dang mtsho ltar zab cing rgya che
NK047(tsi)006:11184: ba nyid phyogs ris su ma chad par rdzogs par
NK047(tsi)006:11185: khong du bskyil ba ni rgya gar du'ang dkon na
NK047(tsi)006:11187: des na 'phags yul nyid na shing rta'i lugs srol so so ba skyong ba de'i tshe na /
NK047(tsi)006:11188: slob dpon 'di nyid kyis zab pa dang rgya che
NK047(tsi)006:11189: ba gnyis ka theg pa chen po'i khyad chos med
NK047(tsi)006:11190: du mi rung ba yin pas tshul gnyis shing rta'i
NK047(tsi)006:11191: lam srol gzhung gcig tu bskyil ba 'di ni gzhan
NK047(tsi)006:11192: las ches khyad par du 'phags pa yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11193: de bas na tshul 'di lta bu'i gzhung bzung ba ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11194: dper na shing rta bzang po la zhon pa lta bu'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11195: de'ang shing rta dang ji ltar 'dra na /
NK047(tsi)006:11196: spyir theg pa ni bzhon pa dang 'dra ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11197: de la gnas na rang 'dod pa'i 'bras bu la phyin par byed pa yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11198: de las theg pa chen po ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11200: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te /
NK047(tsi)006:11201: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK047(tsi)006:11202: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan zlo /
NK047(tsi)006:11204: mkha' 'dra zab pa stong nyid nyi shu dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11205: gzhal med khang 'dra ba rgya che ba'i bkod pas
NK047(tsi)006:11206: mngon par mdzes pa ni theg pa chen po zhes
NK047(tsi)006:11207: gsungs pa de bzhin du 'dir yang bzhon pa gzhan
NK047(tsi)006:11208: las 'phags shing / chen po la 'os pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11210: 'byor ba'i khyad par du ma dang bcas te 'gro ba sogs kyis shing rta'i tshul dang 'dra bar /
NK047(tsi)006:11211: phyogs re re 'dzin pa las 'phags shing /
NK047(tsi)006:11212: zab cing rgya che ba gnyis ka'i blo ldan chen po la 'os pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11213: bden gnyis kyi de kho na nyid zung du chud
NK047(tsi)006:11214: pas sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang sgrub pa la dka'
NK047(tsi)006:11215: ba med pa / tha snyad kyi tshad ma dang
NK047(tsi)006:11216: don dam pa'i tshad ma ste rigs pa'i rnam pa
NK047(tsi)006:11217: tshad med pa'i dga' bde'i 'byor ba chen po dang
NK047(tsi)006:11218: bcas te gnas pa sogs yin pa'i phyir na shing
NK047(tsi)006:11219: ba med pa / rta dang 'dra'o // de 'dra
NK047(tsi)006:11220: ba'i gzhung la gnas pa'i tshe na'ang rigs pa tshad
NK047(tsi)006:11221: mas gzhung gi don nyams su bstar dgos pa yin
NK047(tsi)006:11222: ba med pa / rta dang 'dra'o // te / rang 'grel las /
NK047(tsi)006:11223: de la lung dngos po'i stobs kyis zhugs pa'i rjes
NK047(tsi)006:11224: su dpags pa dang bral ba ni dad pas rjes
NK047(tsi)006:11225: su 'brangs pa dag kyang shin tu yongs su tshim
NK047(tsi)006:11227: gzhung de nyid la dad pas mi mos pa dag lta ci smos /
NK047(tsi)006:11228: dad pa'i sgo nas lung de la rjes su zhugs
NK047(tsi)006:11229: kyang rigs pa dang bral na de'i don rang gi
NK047(tsi)006:11230: nyams su bstar ba'i nges pa rnyed nas yongs su
NK047(tsi)006:11232: zas dang rin po che sna tshogs pa zhen pas
NK047(tsi)006:11233: bcings kyang de dag longs spyod ma shes pa lta
NK047(tsi)006:11234: bu'o // des na shing rta 'dren pa'i rta de
NK047(tsi)006:11235: nyid kha lo gang du sgyur ba srab skyogs la
NK047(tsi)006:11237: dngos stobs kyi rigs pas gang grub pa de nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11238: las gzhan du drang mi nus par lam de dang
NK047(tsi)006:11239: der nges shes kyis 'jug pas na /
NK047(tsi)006:11240: tha snyad dang don dam la dpyod pa'i rigs pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11241: srab skyogs g.yas g.yon gnyis la 'ju bar byed pa
NK047(tsi)006:11242: de ni / zab cing rgya che ba'i don la
NK047(tsi)006:11243: tshad ma gnyis kyi nges pas 'jug pa yin pas
NK047(tsi)006:11244: theg pa chen po pa zhes pa'i ming don dang
NK047(tsi)006:11246: theg pa chen po ni zab cing rgya che ba gnyis ldan yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11247: de la mos pa tsam min par tshad ma gnyis
NK047(tsi)006:11248: kyi sgo nas nges pa'i gang zag yin pa'i phyir
NK047(tsi)006:11249: na / gang theg chen de dang ldan pa la bdag sgra sbyar te theg chen pa zhes so //
NK047(tsi)006:11250: des na 'thad pa dang bral ba'i lugs kyang zhen ltas 'dzin pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11251: 'thad ldan gzhan gyi lugs la sun ci phyin byas
NK047(tsi)006:11252: na bstan pa nyid la phangs pa'i sems su ma
NK047(tsi)006:11253: byas par gyur pas na dngos stobs kyi rigs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11254: dri med dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bstan pa'i rjes
NK047(tsi)006:11255: su zhugs pa'i blo ldan rnams kyis ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11256: bstan pa nyid kyi dbang du byas te rnam par
NK047(tsi)006:11257: dpyod pa drang pos tshul bzhin dpyad par bya ste
NK047(tsi)006:11259: bstan bcos las dpyad rtsod la chags pa'i phyir //
NK047(tsi)006:11260: ma mdzad rnam grol phyir ni de nyid bstan //
NK047(tsi)006:11261: gal te de nyid rnam par bshad pa na //
NK047(tsi)006:11262: gzhan gzhung 'jig par 'gyur na nyes pa med //
NK047(tsi)006:11263: ces pa la sogs pa bzhin yin zhing chos srung ba dang gzung ba'i mchog dam par 'gyur ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11264: gnyis pa tshul gnyis kyi lam de la basngagasa pa la /
NK047(tsi)006:11265: kun gyi thun mong min pa'i yon tan dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11266: de la brten nas dkar chos gzhan skye ba'i yon tan gnyis /
NK047(tsi)006:11268: khyab dang dbang la sogs ma myangs //
NK047(tsi)006:11269: dpag tu med par gnas pa'i rgyu //
NK047(tsi)006:11270: 'jig rten spyi bor gyur pas kyang //
NK047(tsi)006:11271: shin tu myangs pa ma yin pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11272: yang dag bdud rtsi dag pa 'di //
NK047(tsi)006:11273: thugs rje dag pa'i rgyu can gyi //
NK047(tsi)006:11274: de bzhin gshegs pa ma gtogs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11275: gzhan gyi longs spyod ma yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11277: de lta bu'i tshul gnyis po de ni gzhan gyi spyod yul thun mong ba ma yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11278: 'di ltar 'jig rten na che zhing blo gros gsal bar gyur pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11280: tshangs pa dang ser skya la sogas pas phyogs tsam yang ma myangsa pa yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11281: der ma zad yon tan gyi mtha' blos dapaga tu med par gansa par byed pa'i rgyu 'di ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11282: 'jiga rten pa kun gyi spyi bor gyur pa 'jig
NK047(tsi)006:11283: rten 'das pa'i lam can nyan rang 'phags pa rnams
NK047(tsi)006:11284: kyis kyang / shina tu myangsa pa ma yina pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11285: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs ma nor ba bden pa
NK047(tsi)006:11286: gnyis kyi bduda rtsi skyon mtha' dag gis daga pa
NK047(tsi)006:11287: 'di ni / 'gro ba kun la brtse ba'i thugas
NK047(tsi)006:11288: rje chen po sgrib gnyis kyi dri mas yongs su
NK047(tsi)006:11290: de bzhina gshegas pa 'ba' zhig ma gtogsa pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11291: gazhana gyi longas spyod du 'gyur ba ma yina no //
NK047(tsi)006:11293: de la rnam dor te tshangs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11294: khyab 'jug gam nor lha'i bu dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11295: mig mi bzang ngam dbang phyug la sogs pas tshul
NK047(tsi)006:11296: gnyis kyang bshad pa'i phyir 'di dang 'dra'o snyam na
NK047(tsi)006:11297: ma yin te / de dag gis bshad pa nyi tshe ba'i stong pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11298: 'di ltar rnam 'dor gyis bshad pa rnam rig tsam gyi tshul ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11299: bdud rtsi'i thigs pa gsang ba las bstan pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11300: rnam rig tsam ni rtag tu rnam par dag /
NK047(tsi)006:11301: 'di ltar sangs rgyas rtag tu grol ba yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11302: blang dang dor ba med ces rab brtags la //
NK047(tsi)006:11303: tshangs pa mya ngan med par rtag gnas byos //
NK047(tsi)006:11304: zhes don gyi rnam rig tsam gyi rang bzhin gyi bdag tshangs pa mya ngan med pa'am /
NK047(tsi)006:11305: rnam par grol ba rtag pa'i 'bras bu de don du gnyer bya yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11307: rnam rig tsam gyi rang bzhin de ni rtag tu rang bzhin gyis dag pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11308: ma rig pa'i gnyid dang bral ba'i sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11309: 'dod chags sogs kyi 'ching ba las grol ba yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11310: de dag ni don dam yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11311: ma rig pa dang chags sogs glo bur ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11312: des na 'di las ma gtogs pa'i blang dor ci'ang
NK047(tsi)006:11313: med par brtags pa'am shes par byas nas bsgom par
NK047(tsi)006:11315: gzhan yang de'i phyogs su gtogs pa ser skya'i gzhung ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11316: yon tan rnams kyi rang bzhin mchog /
NK047(tsi)006:11317: mthong ba'i lam du 'gror ma yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11318: mthong ba'i lam du gang gyur de //
NK047(tsi)006:11319: sgyu ma lta bur shin tu gsog /
NK047(tsi)006:11320: ces rdul mun snying stobs mnyam pa'i gtso bo ni
NK047(tsi)006:11321: mig sogs kyis mthong ba'i lam du mi 'gyur ba'i
NK047(tsi)006:11322: rang bzhin nam gtso bo don dam /
NK047(tsi)006:11323: mthong ba'i lam du 'gyur ba'i gzugs la sogs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11324: rnam 'gyur thams cad brdzun pa sgyu ma lta bu'o
NK047(tsi)006:11326: bdag shes rig gi skyes bu tsam mthar thug gi 'bras bur 'dod do //
NK047(tsi)006:11328: phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad shes pa rtag pa gcig kho na'i rang bzhin du blta ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11330: bum pa la sogs zhig pa na //
NK047(tsi)006:11331: bum pa'i nam mkha' la sogs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11334: gzugs dang 'bras bur rab brjod pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11335: de dang der ni tha dad kyang //
NK047(tsi)006:11336: nam mkha' la ni tha dad med //
NK047(tsi)006:11337: de bzhin srog kyang nges pa yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11338: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar //
NK047(tsi)006:11339: gzugs zhes pa phyi'i gzugs la sogs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11340: 'bras bu ni nang gi lus te /
NK047(tsi)006:11341: de ltar phyi nang gi snang ba sna tshogs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11342: dag kyang nam mkha'i ngang du ma 'dus pa mi
NK047(tsi)006:11343: srid cing / nam mkha' la tha dad med pa ltar /
NK047(tsi)006:11344: srog gam bdag chen po de'i ngang du gcig par 'dod cing /
NK047(tsi)006:11345: dag dang ma dag sna tshogs su snang ba ni
NK047(tsi)006:11346: med bzhin 'khrul ba thag pa la sbrul 'dzin dang
NK047(tsi)006:11347: / rmi lam lta bu'o zhes zer zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11348: bdag ni bden par rtog gyur pas //
NK047(tsi)006:11349: gang tshe kun tu mi rtog pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11350: de tshe yid ni med 'gyur te //
NK047(tsi)006:11351: gzung ba med pas de 'dzin med //
NK047(tsi)006:11353: rig byed mtha' la nges rnams kyis //
NK047(tsi)006:11354: rmi lam sgyu ma ji 'dra dang //
NK047(tsi)006:11355: dri za'i grong khyer ji 'dra mthong //
NK047(tsi)006:11357: 'gog pa med cing skye ba med //
NK047(tsi)006:11358: bcing ba med cing sgrub pa med //
NK047(tsi)006:11359: thar 'dod med cing thar pa med //
NK047(tsi)006:11360: 'di ni don dam nyid yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11361: chags dang 'jigs dang khro bral ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11362: rig byed mthar phyin thub rnams kyis //
NK047(tsi)006:11363: spros pa nyer zhi gnyis med pa'i //
NK047(tsi)006:11364: rnam par mi rtog 'di mthong ngo //
NK047(tsi)006:11366: 'di dag thams cad ni mdor bsdus na rnam par
NK047(tsi)006:11367: rig pa tsam gyi rang bzhin gyi rtag bdag smra
NK047(tsi)006:11368: ba las ma 'das pas mi 'thad par gong du
NK047(tsi)006:11369: bstan zin la / sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11370: rnam par mi rtog pa la sogs pa ji skad
NK047(tsi)006:11371: brjod pa de bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rab spros
NK047(tsi)006:11372: pa'i dri ma thams cad dang bral ba la de
NK047(tsi)006:11374: de dag gi lugs la de ltar brjod kyang rang
NK047(tsi)006:11375: gi grub mtha' sun 'byin pa tsam du zad do
NK047(tsi)006:11376: // yang khyab 'jug gis bshad pa dbu ma'i lugs ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11378: ming tsam las ni rab 'das shing //
NK047(tsi)006:11379: dngos dang dngos med rnam par spangs //
NK047(tsi)006:11380: 'byung dang bsdu las nges grol ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11381: de ni nor lha'i bu zhes bya //
NK047(tsi)006:11382: dngos la dngos nyid yod ma yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11383: dngos med la yang dngos nyid med //
NK047(tsi)006:11384: dngos dang dngos med rnam grol ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11385: gang de shes de rig byed rig /
NK047(tsi)006:11386: ces rig byed dam tshangs pa'am nor lha'i bu bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11387: dam pa de ni tha snyad kyi ming tsam las
NK047(tsi)006:11388: kyang 'das shing / gzugs la sogs pa'i dngos dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11389: de med pa'i dngos med gnyis ka spangs pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11390: 'byung ba skye ba dang bsdu ba ste 'jig pa las grol ba'i rtag pa yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11391: des na tha snyad las 'das pa de'i rang bzhin
NK047(tsi)006:11392: las ma gtogs pa'i gzugs la sogs pa'i dngos po
NK047(tsi)006:11393: la dngos nyid med de de brdzun pa'i phyir ro
NK047(tsi)006:11394: // dngos po ma grub na de la ltos pa'i dngos med kyang med la /
NK047(tsi)006:11395: de ltar dngos dngos med gnyis dang bral ba'i bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11396: dam pa de shes pa ni rig byed dam tshangs
NK047(tsi)006:11397: pa shes pa yin no zhe'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11398: yang mig mi bzang gis bshad pa dbu ma'i tshul ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11399: zhi ba'i mdzes pa sbyar ba'i gzhung gi pha dang bu'i sbyar ba las /
NK047(tsi)006:11400: bu gcig tshangs pa mchog tu bden //
NK047(tsi)006:11401: rig pa'i dbang phyug mu mtha' yas //
NK047(tsi)006:11402: 'ba' zhig yod pa nyid smra ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11403: de yang zhags par rab tu brjod //
NK047(tsi)006:11404: ces bu gcig ces bos nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11405: tshangs pa de kho na mchog tu bden gyi gzhan thams cad brdzun pa'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11406: gang de ni rig pa'i dbang phyug yin cing thams cad la khyab pa'i mu mtha' yas pa'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11407: de lta mod kyi skye bo gang gis de 'ba' zhig yod pa nyid du smra zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11408: de la ji tsam yod do snyam du mngon par
NK047(tsi)006:11409: zhen pa de tsam du de'ang 'ching ba'i rgyu yin
NK047(tsi)006:11410: pa'i phyir zhags pa dang 'dra bas zhags par rab
NK047(tsi)006:11412: lugs de dag kyang mtha' dang bral ba skad du 'chad kyang /
NK047(tsi)006:11413: mthar gtugs na bdag gam tshangs pa sogs blo yi
NK047(tsi)006:11414: gtad so zhig la mu brten nas yod pas dbu
NK047(tsi)006:11415: ma'i tshul ga la yin te rgyas par bkag zin
NK047(tsi)006:11416: to // des na rdzogs pa chen po shin tu
NK047(tsi)006:11417: zab mo'i mthar thug pa yin slad rtogs dka' bas
NK047(tsi)006:11418: to // na / thos bsam gyi gnas lugs la sgro 'dogs chod pa mthar phyin pa'am /
NK047(tsi)006:11419: zab mo'i man ngag gi gnad dang ldan par ma
NK047(tsi)006:11420: gyur pa'i blun sgom gyis bsgoms pa phal che ba
NK047(tsi)006:11422: ka dag la nges pa ma rnyed par yod pa'ang
NK047(tsi)006:11423: min la med pa'ang min pa'i gzhi zhig snying la
NK047(tsi)006:11424: brnag pa tsam gyis ni gar yang mi phyin te
NK047(tsi)006:11425: / de 'dra ba'i yod med gnyis kyis stong pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11426: stong gzhi logs su ngo bos grub par bzung na
NK047(tsi)006:11427: / / de'i ming la bsam mi khyab pa'i bdag gam /
NK047(tsi)006:11431: ye shes sogs ji btags kyang ming tsam las don 'dra ba yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11432: mtha' bzhi'i spros bral gyi gnas lugs so so rang
NK047(tsi)006:11433: gis rig par bya ba'i 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen
NK047(tsi)006:11434: po ni de 'dra ba zhig yin tshod mi gda'
NK047(tsi)006:11435: bas yang dag pa'i lam dang ston pa la brten
NK047(tsi)006:11436: pa gal che'o // des na tshig tsam la sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11439: rigs pas drangs pa'i nges shes phu thag chod pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11440: sgo nas nyi tshe ba'i stong pa mu stegs rnams
NK047(tsi)006:11441: kyi bla na 'phags pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i stong
NK047(tsi)006:11442: pa nyid kyi tshul ma shes na ci'ang mi phan
NK047(tsi)006:11443: la / shes na sangs rgyas kyis gang gsungs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11444: 'di ni khyab 'jug la sogs pa de dag gis
NK047(tsi)006:11445: cung zad kyang ma myangs te /
NK047(tsi)006:11446: de dag gis rnam rig dang dbu ma'i lugs bshad pa ni ming tsam du shes par 'gyur ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11447: de ltar phyi nang gi grub mtha' 'di tshig tsam
NK047(tsi)006:11448: gyis phye mi nus par zab mo'i gnad gnam sa
NK047(tsi)006:11449: ltar mi mtshungs pa yod pas /
NK047(tsi)006:11450: jo bo rjes kyang khong bod du byon rjes da
NK047(tsi)006:11451: lta rgya gar na phyi nang gi grub mtha' phye
NK047(tsi)006:11452: nus pa dka' gsungs pa ltar /
NK047(tsi)006:11453: bod du'ang ban+de dang bon po yang de dang 'dra'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11454: de ltar phyi rol pa'i 'dod pa'i gzhung gi tshigs
NK047(tsi)006:11455: bcad cung zad rang 'grel na bkod pa ka ma
NK047(tsi)006:11456: la sh+ai la'i dka' 'grel gyis bshad pa ltar 'dir
NK047(tsi)006:11459: khyab dang dbang la sogs ma myangs //
NK047(tsi)006:11460: zhes pa'i don bshad zin to //
NK047(tsi)006:11461: de nas dpag tu med par gnas pa'i rgyu zhes pa tha snyad kyis dpag tu med pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11462: ji ltar dpag tu med na de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'od zer gcig dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11463: ba spu'i bu ga gcig la'ang phyogs 'di tsam zhes pa'i tshad dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11464: dus 'di tsam du'o zhes pa'i tshad gzung mi nus pa chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par 'jug pa'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11465: de lta bu'i dpag tu med pa'i chos nyid de
NK047(tsi)006:11466: lta bu la gnas par byed pa'i rgyu ni chos
NK047(tsi)006:11467: kyi dbyings dang rjes su mthun pa bden gnyis zung
NK047(tsi)006:11468: du 'jug pa'i dbu ma'i tshul la gnas pas so
NK047(tsi)006:11469: // de'ang dper na phyogs gcig gi dbang du byas na /
NK047(tsi)006:11470: de bzhin gshegs pa dus dpag tu med pa 'khor
NK047(tsi)006:11471: ba ji srid du bzhugs par byed pa'i rgyu ni
NK047(tsi)006:11472: / srid zhi mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i sher phyin 'di yin pa bzhin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11473: des na zla ba'i 'od zer ltar dag pa bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11474: med pa gnyis kyi rang bzhin nyi tshe ba ma
NK047(tsi)006:11475: yin pa'i stong pa nyid kyi bdud rtsi 'di sngon
NK047(tsi)006:11476: gyi tshe skyob pa bcom ldan 'das nyid kyis shin
NK047(tsi)006:11477: tu gsol te / rgyu des rnam pa thams cad
NK047(tsi)006:11478: kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i shes rab dang thugs rje'i
NK047(tsi)006:11480: sgrib pa gnyis kyi phung po ma lus pa dang bral ba /
NK047(tsi)006:11481: sems can thams cad kyi mchog nyid du 'khor ba ji srid du bzhugs pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11482: sems can kun mchog nyid sems dang //
NK047(tsi)006:11483: spang dang rtogs dang gsum po la //
NK047(tsi)006:11484: chen po gsum gyi rang byung gi /
NK047(tsi)006:11485: ched du bya ba 'di shes bya //
NK047(tsi)006:11487: de'ang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags de las phra ba
NK047(tsi)006:11488: med pa'i mthar thug pa lta bu ma rig bag
NK047(tsi)006:11490: las dang phung po sdug bsngal gyi rtsa ba gtan nas yongs zad du byed pa la /
NK047(tsi)006:11492: yid kyi rang bzhin gyi lus dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11493: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'chi 'pho ba dag kyang
NK047(tsi)006:11494: log pas phyogs dus mnyam pa nyid ye shes kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11495: sku skye 'gag dang rtag mi rtag yod med la
NK047(tsi)006:11496: sogs pa'i mtha' thams cad spangs pa'i sangs rgyas 'ba'
NK047(tsi)006:11497: zhig 'grub pa'o // ci'i phyir yang dag pa'i lam la bdud rtsi zhes brjod snyam na /
NK047(tsi)006:11498: gtan du 'chi ba med pa'i rang bzhin du byed pas de skad du brjod de /
NK047(tsi)006:11499: de'ang bdud rtsi 'ba' zhig ma gtogs rnyog ma'i bsre
NK047(tsi)006:11500: bslad med pas yongs su dag pa la bdud rtsi
NK047(tsi)006:11502: de la kha cig 'di snyam du /
NK047(tsi)006:11503: dpag tu med par gnas pa'i rgyu //
NK047(tsi)006:11505: yang dag bdud rtsi zhes sogs kyi tshig rkang 'di'i gong du bkod na 'gyur mi bade'am snyam na /
NK047(tsi)006:11506: sngon gyi lo pan chen po rnams ni bsam bzhin
NK047(tsi)006:11507: sprul pa'i gang zag ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan
NK047(tsi)006:11508: pa yin pas tshig 'di dag gi go rim tsam
NK047(tsi)006:11509: la'ang nus pa zhig 'don rgyu yod pas de ltar
NK047(tsi)006:11510: bsgyur ba ste / de'ang dus lta bu la mtshon
NK047(tsi)006:11511: na sangs rgyas ni srid pa ji srid par 'khor
NK047(tsi)006:11512: bsgyur ba ste / bar bzhugs la / nyan rang gis de mi nus te /
NK047(tsi)006:11513: mi nus pa'i rgyu mtshan yang srid zhi mnyam nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11514: du rtogs pa'i shes rab med pas 'khor ba la
NK047(tsi)006:11515: 'jigs pa dang / zhi ba la dga' ba'i yid dang ldan pas yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11516: gzhan yang bsam mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos
NK047(tsi)006:11517: rdzogs par brnyes mi nus pa thams cad bden gnyis
NK047(tsi)006:11518: zung 'jug dbu ma'i tshul 'di lta bu ma shes
NK047(tsi)006:11520: zhes pa sogs kyi tshig gi nus pa khongs nas 'don pa'i ched yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11521: de ltar na 'jig rten pa'i spyi bor gyur pa nyan rang dag gis kyang ma myangs na /
NK047(tsi)006:11522: 'jig rten pa tshangs dbang khyab 'jug la sogs pas lta ci smos zhes /
NK047(tsi)006:11523: 'dir shin tu rab tu sogs basngagasa pa'i yul kho na la sbyor dgos pa ma yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11524: brjod bya gang la sbyar ba de nyid lhag par brnan pa'i don yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11525: thugs rje dag pa zhes sogs kyi thugs rje ni
NK047(tsi)006:11526: 'gro ba kun la brtse ba chen pos nyid kyis
NK047(tsi)006:11527: ji ltar gzigs pa'i lam ston pa yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11528: thugs rje chen po de'ang gzigs pa rab rib kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11529: dri ma mtha' dag dang bral ba ni dag pa'o
NK047(tsi)006:11530: // de lta bu'i thugs rje chen po yongs su
NK047(tsi)006:11531: dag pa'i rgyu sngon du song ba can nam 'bras
NK047(tsi)006:11532: bu ni de bzhin gshegs pa yin la de kho
NK047(tsi)006:11533: nas bden gnyis kyi bdud rtsi 'di gsol to //
NK047(tsi)006:11535: de la mkhas pa rnams kyis gang bshad pa dngos
NK047(tsi)006:11536: stobs kyi rigs pa dang 'brel pa kho na yin
NK047(tsi)006:11537: pas / 'dir yang tshig 'di nyid kyi nus pas
NK047(tsi)006:11538: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis gzhan la lam ston
NK047(tsi)006:11540: gzigs pa rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyis bstan
NK047(tsi)006:11541: pa'i lam dri ma med pa 'di lta bu ni
NK047(tsi)006:11542: / bden gnyis ma nor ba'i tshul la yang dag
NK047(tsi)006:11543: par zhugs pa'i rgyu sngon du song ba yin pas
NK047(tsi)006:11544: / / yang dag pa'i tshul gnyis po 'di sangs
NK047(tsi)006:11545: rgyas nyid las gzhan gyi yul min par 'bras bu'i
NK047(tsi)006:11546: rtags kyis rjes su dpogs pa la sogs pa'i don
NK047(tsi)006:11547: ches mang po zhig bstan pa yin mod kyi /
NK047(tsi)006:11548: tshig 'di rnams sgroms che bas zhib tu nus pa
NK047(tsi)006:11549: bton te bshad na yig tshogs lci bar 'gyur bas
NK047(tsi)006:11550: ma smos so // gnyis pa la /
NK047(tsi)006:11551: sems can la snying rje dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11552: ston pa la gus pa skye ba'i phan yon gnyis /
NK047(tsi)006:11554: de phyir log par bstan pa yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11555: grub mthar 'chel ba'i blo can la //
NK047(tsi)006:11556: de lugs rjes 'jug blo can rnams //
NK047(tsi)006:11557: snying rje nyid ni rab tu skye //
NK047(tsi)006:11559: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa las gzhan gyis lam
NK047(tsi)006:11560: 'di ston mi nus pa de yi phyir phyi rol
NK047(tsi)006:11561: pa'i ston pa rnams kyis lam yang dag pa ma
NK047(tsi)006:11562: yin pa loga para bstana pa yi grub mathara zhen
NK047(tsi)006:11563: pa'am 'chela ba'i blo can rnams la /
NK047(tsi)006:11564: de bzhin gshegs pa de yi lugs dam pa'i rjesa su 'juga pa'i blo can rnams ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11565: kye ma lam 'dod pa gang dag lam log par
NK047(tsi)006:11566: gyur pa 'di dag snying re rje snyam du snying
NK047(tsi)006:11567: rje shugs drag po nyid ni raba tu skye ba
NK047(tsi)006:11568: yin no // de la 'di ltar gzhan gyi lugs la brtags na /
NK047(tsi)006:11569: nyi ma'i 'od zer shin tu rno ba dag /
NK047(tsi)006:11570: kha ba'i dum bu la sgrib pa med par babs pa bzhin du /
NK047(tsi)006:11571: pha rol po'i 'dod pa gting mi tshugs par mthong zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11572: lta ba des de dag bslus par shes nas brtse ba 'phel zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11573: des mtshon te rang gis de kho na nyid gtan
NK047(tsi)006:11574: la phebs pa na gzhan yang dag pa'i lam dang
NK047(tsi)006:11575: bral bas srid pa na yang yang skye zhing mgon
NK047(tsi)006:11576: med pa rnams la'ang snying rje chen po mi mthun
NK047(tsi)006:11577: pa'i phyogs chung ngu dang yang ma 'dres pa ngang
NK047(tsi)006:11578: gis skye zhing tshad med par 'phel bar 'gyur te
NK047(tsi)006:11579: / snying rje chen po'i rgyu bdag gzhan mnyam pa
NK047(tsi)006:11580: nyid du rtog cing gzhan rmongs pa'i sdug bsngal la
NK047(tsi)006:11582: snying rje'i gegs kun nas mnar sems pa sogs kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11583: gzhir gyur pa bdag rtog gi dri ma bral ba'i
NK047(tsi)006:11584: phyir / rgyu tshang zhing gegs med pa'i rigs pas kyang grub bo //
NK047(tsi)006:11585: de la snying rje'i rigs kyi gzhi bzung nas 'gro ba rnams khur du khyer ba /
NK047(tsi)006:11586: rang don yid byed dang mtshan ma'i dmigs pa'i dri dang bral ba la /
NK047(tsi)006:11587: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa snying rje'i rigs kyi khyim khas len pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11588: skyes bu'i ljid khyer ba yang dag pa'i brtse ba can zhes bya'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11589: de ltar na gzhan sdug bsngal dang bral bar 'dod pa'i snying rje ldan pa gang gis /
NK047(tsi)006:11590: sdug bsngal dang de'i rgyu 'phel bar mthong na snying
NK047(tsi)006:11591: rje lhag par 'phel te bud shing bsnan pa'i me
NK047(tsi)006:11592: bzhin no // de 'ang don dam pa'i chos la
NK047(tsi)006:11593: sdang ba rnams ni sdug bsngal gyi rgyu'i mchog la
NK047(tsi)006:11594: bzhin no // gnas pa ste / 'di ltar nya
NK047(tsi)006:11595: dang bya la sogs pa gsod pa sogs ni bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11596: dang gzhan gyi dgra chen po ma yin te /
NK047(tsi)006:11597: de dag ni ma bsad kyang rlung gis bskyod nas chu'i chu bur ltar shin tu mi rtag pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11598: bdag la phan pa cung zad kyang mi nus pa'i lus rnag can /
NK047(tsi)006:11599: grangs yod pa zhig gsod par zad la /
NK047(tsi)006:11600: don dam pa'i chos la sdang ba dag ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11601: 'khor ba ji srid bar bzhugs pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11602: bdag gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pas mdzes pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11603: grangs las 'das pa'i rgyal ba dang 'brel ba'i chos kyi sku la gnod pa ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11604: chos sku de'i sa bon de kho na nyid la mos pa la gnod par zhugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK047(tsi)006:11605: de nyid kyi phyir dam pa'i chos spangs pa'i rnam
NK047(tsi)006:11606: smin shin tu mi bzad pa rnam pa mang du
NK047(tsi)006:11608: de skad du'ang slob dpon klus /
NK047(tsi)006:11609: shin tu rgya che rab zab la //
NK047(tsi)006:11610: sgyid lug shin tu ma sbyangs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11611: bdag gzhan dgra dag gti mug gis //
NK047(tsi)006:11612: da ltar theg pa che la smod //
NK047(tsi)006:11613: ces gsungs pa la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11614: des na rigs dang blo ma sbyangs pa'i gang zag
NK047(tsi)006:11615: rnams ji lta ji ltar zab pa'i theg pa chen
NK047(tsi)006:11616: po la de lta de ltar skrag cing smod pa
NK047(tsi)006:11618: rang nyid kyi nyams dang sbyar ba'i sher phyin ltar snang la brten nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11619: zab cing dpags par dka' ba'i sher phyin la 'di
NK047(tsi)006:11620: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa min no zhes sogs sun
NK047(tsi)006:11621: 'byin pa mang du 'byung bar gsungs la /
NK047(tsi)006:11623: dman par mos shing khams kyang shin tu dman //
NK047(tsi)006:11624: grogs po dman pa dag gis yongs bskor ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11625: zab cing rgya che legs par bshad pa'i chos //
NK047(tsi)006:11626: 'di la gal te mos med grub pa yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11627: zhes gsungs pa ltar zab pa'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyis
NK047(tsi)006:11628: blo yul du ma gyur nas theg chen la sdang
NK047(tsi)006:11629: ba rnams la snying rje chen pos rjes su bzung
NK047(tsi)006:11632: blo nor ldan pas lugs gzhan la //
NK047(tsi)006:11633: ji ltar snying po med mthong ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11634: de ltar de dag skyob pa la //
NK047(tsi)006:11635: gus pa shin tu skye bar 'gyur //
NK047(tsi)006:11637: 'phags nor gyi phul du gyur pa blo shes rab
NK047(tsi)006:11638: kyi nora dang ldana pasa bstan pa 'di las phyi
NK047(tsi)006:11639: rol tu gyur pa'i lugas gazhana la ji ltar snying
NK047(tsi)006:11640: po meda pa mthonga ba de ltar blo ldan skal
NK047(tsi)006:11641: bzang de daga / lam 'di ni bcom ldan 'das kho nas bstan to snyam du /
NK047(tsi)006:11642: bdag cag gi ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas skyob pa nyid la /
NK047(tsi)006:11643: gusa pa shiina tu skye bar 'gyur te /
NK047(tsi)006:11644: tsha bas ji lta ji ltar gdung ba de tsam
NK047(tsi)006:11645: du bsil ba'i chu la dga' ba 'phel ba bzhin
NK047(tsi)006:11646: no // de'ang 'di ltar gzhan gyi lugs ni rigs
NK047(tsi)006:11647: ngan blun po'i skye bo la'ang grags pa'i yul rags
NK047(tsi)006:11649: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab thog ma dang bar dang tha mar dge ba /
NK047(tsi)006:11650: gser bzang po lta bur bsregs pa dang bcad pa
NK047(tsi)006:11651: dang bdar ba dang 'dra ba'i mngon sum dang rjes
NK047(tsi)006:11652: dpags dang / rang gi tshig rnams kyis gnod par
NK047(tsi)006:11653: ma gyur pa'i dpyad gsum gyis dag pa de ni
NK047(tsi)006:11654: shin tu thib po dang ldan pa'i 'khor ba na
NK047(tsi)006:11655: ma 'dres pa'i ye shes kyis de kho na nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11656: la cung zad kyang 'khrugs pa'am rnyog pa med par
NK047(tsi)006:11657: dpags dang / mthong nas / mi dang lha yul
NK047(tsi)006:11658: ba'i gtso bo mtha' dag gi cod pan gyi phreng
NK047(tsi)006:11659: dpags dang / mthong nas / bas / zhabs pad+ma
NK047(tsi)006:11660: gnyis mdzes par byas pa dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten
NK047(tsi)006:11661: gyi bla ma sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11662: shes pa su zhig don dam par mngon par ma
NK047(tsi)006:11663: zhen pa'i tshul gyis sgrub pa snying por byed pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11664: dad pa ci phyir mi bskyed de bskyed par rigs
NK047(tsi)006:11665: dpags dang / mthong nas / bas / so //
NK047(tsi)006:11666: de ltar na yang dag pa'i lta ba de las
NK047(tsi)006:11667: sems can la snying rje skye zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11668: snying rje de la'ang sems can tsam la dmigs pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11670: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje gsum gyi nang nas
NK047(tsi)006:11671: gtso bor gyur pa dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje
NK047(tsi)006:11673: lam de nyid ston pa'i sangs rgyas la gus pa skyes pa de la'ang /
NK047(tsi)006:11674: dang 'dod yid ches gsum yod pa'i nang nas rgyal
NK047(tsi)006:11675: po lta bu yid ches kyi dad pa skye bas
NK047(tsi)006:11676: gzhan gnyis kyang 'khor gyi tshul du 'byung ngo //
NK047(tsi)006:11677: mi ldog pa'i dad pa ni yid ches pa mi
NK047(tsi)006:11678: mthun phyogs kyis 'phrog mi nus pa'i khyad par tsam
NK047(tsi)006:11679: yin no // de ltar na dkar po'i chos thams
NK047(tsi)006:11680: cad kyi rtsa ba ni dad pa dang snying rje
NK047(tsi)006:11681: yin no // yin pas / de re re yod
NK047(tsi)006:11682: na rnam byang gi chos thams cad kyang 'byung bar
NK047(tsi)006:11684: shes bya srid zhi gnyis la dmigs pa'i blo yin no cog gi nang na /
NK047(tsi)006:11685: srid pa la dmigs pa la snying rje las bzang ba gzhan med cing /
NK047(tsi)006:11686: zhi ba la dmigs pa'i blo la dad pa las bzang ba med la /
NK047(tsi)006:11687: de gnyis yod par gyur na /
NK047(tsi)006:11688: de gnyis zung du 'brel ba byang chub kyi sems rin po che 'byung ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11689: byang chub kyi sems ni sangs rgyas kyi chos gcig ma zhes grags pa yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11690: de lta bu'i kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems de nyid ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11691: don dam byang chub kyi sems mtshan nyid pa rtogs
NK047(tsi)006:11692: pa'i gang zag la nam yang 'bral mi shes su
NK047(tsi)006:11693: 'byung ste / des dngos po'i gnas tshul ma nor ba mthong ba na /
NK047(tsi)006:11694: rang don yid byed kyi dri ma dang bral te /
NK047(tsi)006:11695: gnas tshul la rmongs pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi don
NK047(tsi)006:11696: du gnas lugs mngon sum mdzad pa'i sangs rgyas 'thob
NK047(tsi)006:11697: 'dod kyi bsam pa nam yang ldog pa mi srid
NK047(tsi)006:11698: la / don dam par ni kun rdzob dang don
NK047(tsi)006:11699: dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems gnyis po ngo bo
NK047(tsi)006:11700: 'du 'bral med par gnas pa nyid gtan la 'bebs
NK047(tsi)006:11701: pa ni sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams nas 'byung ngo
NK047(tsi)006:11702: la / // de ltar na stong pa nyid dang
NK047(tsi)006:11703: snying rje zung du 'jug pas sa dang lam gyi
NK047(tsi)006:11705: rang don du chos kyi sku dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11706: gzhan don du gzugs kyi sku ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11707: sku gnyis zung du 'jug pa brnyes nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11708: nam mkha' ji srid du phrin las rgyun mi 'chad
NK047(tsi)006:11709: pa 'bad rtsol med bzhin par yid bzhin gyi nor
NK047(tsi)006:11710: bu dang / dpag bsam gyi shing bzhin du 'gro
NK047(tsi)006:11711: ba rnams kyi gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dgos
NK047(tsi)006:11712: pa yid bzhin du stsol ba yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11713: de'ang sku gnyis po gtso che chung gi sgo nas rang don gzhan don zhes bzhag kyang /
NK047(tsi)006:11714: don du ngo bo zung 'jug 'bral mi shes pa'i ye shes kyi sku yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11716: yang dag shes tshol sngon btang ste //
NK047(tsi)006:11717: don dam rnam par nges gyur nas //
NK047(tsi)006:11718: lta ngan thib gnas 'jig rten la //
NK047(tsi)006:11719: snying rje kun tu bskyed nas su //
NK047(tsi)006:11720: 'gro don byed par dpa' gyur pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11721: byang chub blo rgyas mkhas pa ni //
NK047(tsi)006:11722: blo dang snying rjes brgyan pa yis //
NK047(tsi)006:11723: thub pa'i brtul zhugs yang dag spyod //
NK047(tsi)006:11724: ces sngon du de kho na nyid gtan la phebs
NK047(tsi)006:11725: nas des snying rje chen po drangs te rdzogs byang
NK047(tsi)006:11728: gang dag dad pas rjes 'brang ba //
NK047(tsi)006:11729: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed nas //
NK047(tsi)006:11730: thub pa'i brtul zhugs mngon byas te //
NK047(tsi)006:11731: de ni yang dag shes tshol brtson //
NK047(tsi)006:11732: zhes gsungs pa ltar sngon du snying rjes drangs pas byang chub kyi sems bskyed nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11733: byang chub don gnyer la med du mi rung ba
NK047(tsi)006:11734: yang dag pa'i de kho na nyid tshol bar zhugs
NK047(tsi)006:11736: gang ltar yang kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang
NK047(tsi)006:11737: chub kyi sems rin po che rnam pa gnyis ni
NK047(tsi)006:11738: dngos po'i chos nyid kyis phan tshun gcig grogs su
NK047(tsi)006:11739: gcig 'ong zhing mi 'bral ba yin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11740: ba zhi pa mjug don la /
NK047(tsi)006:11741: slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa'i mdzad byang dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11742: lo pan gang gis bsgyur ba'i 'gyur byang gnyis /
NK047(tsi)006:11744: dbu ma rgyan gyi tshig le'ura byas pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11745: slob dpon zhi ba 'tsho bdag dang gzhan gyi grub pa'i mtha' rgya mtsho'i pha rol tu son pa /
NK047(tsi)006:11746: 'phags pa ngag gi dbang phyug gi zhabs kyi pad+ma
NK047(tsi)006:11747: rnyog pa med pa'i ze'u 'bru spyi bos len pas
NK047(tsi)006:11748: mdzad pa / zhes 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i grub pa'i mtha' dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11749: des mtshon te rig byed kyi gnas rgya mtsho lta
NK047(tsi)006:11750: bu tshad med pa dag la lhag ma cung zad
NK047(tsi)006:11751: kyang med par mkhyen pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11752: rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos las chos gsan par bstan pa'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11753: rdzogs so zhes pa gzhung ma tshang ba med pa'i don to //
NK047(tsi)006:11755: rgya gar gyi mkhan po su ren+d+ra bo d+hi ste lha dbang byang chub dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11756: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba ban+de ye shes sdes tshig rgya skad las bod skad du bsgyur zhing /
NK047(tsi)006:11757: slar yang tshig don gyi cha la dag ther mdzad
NK047(tsi)006:11758: nas zhus te 'chad nyan gyi sgo nas gtan la
NK047(tsi)006:11760: 'di la rje tsong kha pas tshigs bcad lhug gnyis ka rtsa bar bzhed pa ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11761: 'grel pa 'adi'ang shing rta chen po rang gi gsung
NK047(tsi)006:11762: shin tu don gyi myang bya phul du byung ba
NK047(tsi)006:11763: zhig yod pas rtsa 'grel lhan du 'chad nyan byung
NK047(tsi)006:11764: na legs pas rtsa ba yin no zhes gsungs na'ang
NK047(tsi)006:11765: don gyi 'gal ba med pa sogs bdag nyid chen
NK047(tsi)006:11766: po des bstan pa thugs la gzhag pa'i dgos pa
NK047(tsi)006:11767: khyad par ba yod par gdon mi za yang /
NK047(tsi)006:11768: spyir ni don res 'ga' tshigs bcad kyis bstan pa'am /
NK047(tsi)006:11769: res 'ga' tshig lhug pas bstan pa lta bu'i spel ma ma yin par /
NK047(tsi)006:11770: rtsa ba tshigs bcad kyi don de slar yang 'grel
NK047(tsi)006:11771: pas bkrol te bshad pa kho na yin pa 'di
NK047(tsi)006:11772: ltar lags so // des na 'dir rang 'grel nyid
NK047(tsi)006:11773: 'grel pa'i lugs su byas na tshig shin tu mang
NK047(tsi)006:11774: bas gzhan dag 'jug dka' ba'i phyir 'grel pa'i tshig
NK047(tsi)006:11776: don du 'grel ba'i gnad kun gsal por bkrol yod pas /
NK047(tsi)006:11777: 'di la brten te 'grel pa nyid kyi tshig gi nus pa rnams kyang myong nus pas /
NK047(tsi)006:11778: slar yang rang 'grel dang dka' 'grel gnyis la'ang blta bar byas na legs so //
NK047(tsi)006:11779: da ni gong gi sa bcad gnyis pa ni /
NK047(tsi)006:11780: de ltar yon tan gyi khyad par du mas 'phags pa'i gzhung 'di chos can /
NK047(tsi)006:11781: rnam par 'grel zhing bshad pa la dgos pa yod de /
NK047(tsi)006:11782: thun mong dang thun mong min pa'i phan yon gyi khyad par 'thob pa'i phyir /
NK047(tsi)006:11783: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu byi dor byas pa bzhin no //
NK047(tsi)006:11784: de la thun mong du 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11785: bka'i dgongs pa dri ma med pa de dag rigs
NK047(tsi)006:11786: pa'i lam nas drangs te nges pa skye ba'i tshul
NK047(tsi)006:11788: tshul gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i theg pa chen po mtha'
NK047(tsi)006:11789: dag bzung ba'i phan yon la re ba yang dag
NK047(tsi)006:11790: byar yod de / chos gzung ba'i mchog ni rtogs pa'i chos yin la /
NK047(tsi)006:11791: de 'dzin pa ni ji lta ba bzhin du rang
NK047(tsi)006:11792: gis rtogs nas nyams su len pa kho na yin
NK047(tsi)006:11793: pa'i phyir ro // de ltar chos kyi dbyings rnam
NK047(tsi)006:11794: par dag pa la phyin ci log tu rtog pa
NK047(tsi)006:11795: thams cad rigs pa dri ma med pas bsal nas
NK047(tsi)006:11796: pa'i phyir ro // / rang gis rtogs pa ltar
NK047(tsi)006:11797: gzhan la ston par byed pa de'i phan yon kyang
NK047(tsi)006:11798: pa'i phyir ro // / / ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK047(tsi)006:11799: ting 'dzin 'di ni su dag ston byed pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11800: de ni nam yang byang chub the tshom med //
NK047(tsi)006:11801: bsod nams phung po mchog dang gang ldan zhing //
NK047(tsi)006:11802: gang la tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11803: 'jig rten slob dpon sangs rgyas rnam par 'dren //
NK047(tsi)006:11804: rang byung thugs rje chen po ma gtogs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11805: de yi 'og tu sems can su dag kyang //
NK047(tsi)006:11806: stong chen 'di na bsod nams phung po dang //
NK047(tsi)006:11807: mtshungs med bsam gyis mi khyab ye shes kyis //
NK047(tsi)006:11808: mnyam par gyur pa nam yang yod med do //
NK047(tsi)006:11809: zhes pa la sogs pas mtshon te shes par bya'o //
NK047(tsi)006:11810: thun mong ma yin pa'i dbang du na /
NK047(tsi)006:11811: rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs dang ngo bo tha mi dad pa'i shing rta chen po 'dis /
NK047(tsi)006:11812: sus kyang gdul bar dka' ba'i rang re bod yul
NK047(tsi)006:11813: rgyal bstan gyi snang ba dkar pos khyab par mdzad
NK047(tsi)006:11815: thugs rje'i rten 'brel gyis rang cag rnams la lhag par byin rlabs 'jug pa dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11816: khyad par du gzhung tshig tshogs nyung yang rigs pa
NK047(tsi)006:11817: rno la chod che ba phyogs gcig tu snang ba
NK047(tsi)006:11818: 'di 'dra rgya gzhung gzhan na'ang dkon par 'dug pa
NK047(tsi)006:11819: ni mang du brjod pas ci bya ste /
NK047(tsi)006:11820: gser gyi mdangs dang bu ram gyi ro bzhin du
NK047(tsi)006:11821: gzhung mang thos zab rgyas kyi blo can rnams la
NK047(tsi)006:11822: mngon sum grub pa 'di ltar lags pas blo gros
NK047(tsi)006:11823: kyi sgo myur du 'byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11824: mgon po de'i bka' drin rjes su dran nas drin gzo ba la sogs pa'i dgos pa'ang yod do //
NK047(tsi)006:11825: de skad du'ang dpal sa skya pan+di tas /
NK047(tsi)006:11826: sdom brtson dam pa dpal ldan zhi ba 'tsho //
NK047(tsi)006:11827: brtul zhugs grub pa pad+ma sam b+ha wa //
NK047(tsi)006:11828: blo gsal dbang po pad+ma'i ngang tshul sogs //
NK047(tsi)006:11829: snyigs ma'i dus kyi rgyal ba gnyis pa yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11831: rje tsong kha ba chen pos /
NK047(tsi)006:11832: 'jam dpal dbyangs kyis rjes bzung bas //
NK047(tsi)006:11833: rang gzhan grub mtha'i pha rol son //
NK047(tsi)006:11834: zab mo'i don la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11836: mgon des gangs can khrod 'dir rgyal ba'i bstan //
NK047(tsi)006:11837: thog mar legs par btsugs tshe klu sgrub lugs //
NK047(tsi)006:11838: phyogs 'dir dar ba'i rten 'brel legs bsgrigs pas //
NK047(tsi)006:11839: da dung du yang zab mo dbu ma la //
NK047(tsi)006:11840: mos pa'i phyogs 'dzin rgyun mi chad par byung //
NK047(tsi)006:11841: de phyir mkhas pa'i dbang po de yi gzhung //
NK047(tsi)006:11842: bdag cag rnams kyis mi nyams spel ba ni //
NK047(tsi)006:11843: bka' drin gzo ba'i mchod pa bla med yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11844: rnam dpyod nam mkha'i khyon ltar mtha' yas shing //
NK047(tsi)006:11845: dmigs med brtse ba'i stobs ni shugs drag pas //
NK047(tsi)006:11846: yongs su drangs pa'i gzhung mchog dbu ma'i rgyan //
NK047(tsi)006:11847: 'di yi rigs pa'i dga' ston myangs pa na //
NK047(tsi)006:11848: skye ba mang por rigs pa'i lam du ni //
NK047(tsi)006:11849: ngal ba mang byas sgrub dang sun 'byin la //
NK047(tsi)006:11850: legs par byang ba'i rgol ba mkhas mang gi /
NK047(tsi)006:11851: gtsug na gtsug rgyan nor bu ltar mtho bas //
NK047(tsi)006:11852: smra ba ngan pa'i tshogs rnams mthar mdzad pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11853: 'phags pa'i yul na'ang ches dkon 'di 'dra ni //
NK047(tsi)006:11854: bod kyi rje rgyal btsan pos spyan 'drongs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:11855: e ma bdag cag bod 'bangs skal bzang zhes //
NK047(tsi)006:11856: yid ni rmad byung bde la rol pa yis //
NK047(tsi)006:11857: yongs su bskyod pas gzhan gyi dbang gyur pas //
NK047(tsi)006:11858: zhes sogs basngagasa pa rnams ni basngagasa pa'i yul mchog
NK047(tsi)006:11859: gi yon tan mkhyen pa ni basngagasa pa po rang
NK047(tsi)006:11860: nyid rnam thar mchog la gnas pa'i 'bras rtags yin
NK047(tsi)006:11861: te / rin po che'i rin thang ni 'byor ldan
NK047(tsi)006:11862: shes rab dang ldan pa 'ba' zhig gisa shes pa
NK047(tsi)006:11863: te / bzhin no // gzhan yang bka' chems kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11864: yi ge rnying pa rnams nas mkhan chen gyi lugs
NK047(tsi)006:11865: la yid ches shing 'dzin pa yod pa de srid
NK047(tsi)006:11866: du gangs can na bstan pa'i snang ba mi nub
NK047(tsi)006:11868: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i bdag nyid mkhan chen byang chub
NK047(tsi)006:11869: sems dpa' rang nyid kyi zhal gdams mchog gling gter
NK047(tsi)006:11870: byon las kyang / ston pa'i bstan pa rin chen
NK047(tsi)006:11871: 'di gangs can ljongs su ngas gsal bas bdag gi
NK047(tsi)006:11872: rjes su zhugs nas kyang ston pa'i bstan pa mchog
NK047(tsi)006:11873: tu zungs lha cig khri srong lde'u btsan dang rje
NK047(tsi)006:11874: btsun pad+ma sam b+ha wa kho bo bo d+hi sat+wa
NK047(tsi)006:11875: yis bka' khrims bcas pa ji bzhin du tshe dang
NK047(tsi)006:11876: ldan rnams bya dgos so rgyal ba'i bstan pa nyams
NK047(tsi)006:11877: dma' zhing tshe dang ldan pa nyam thag na ston
NK047(tsi)006:11878: pa'i thugs rje bskul bar gyis nga la gsol ba
NK047(tsi)006:11879: yang yang thob phyi ltar 'dul khrims legs par bsrung
NK047(tsi)006:11880: nang ltar byang chub sems 'byongs nas gsang ba sngags
NK047(tsi)006:11881: kyi grub pa brnyes lcang lo can du mngon 'tshang
NK047(tsi)006:11882: rgya gsang ba'i bdag por dbyer med cing sprul pas
NK047(tsi)006:11883: bod kyi bstan pa skyong de phyir byin rlabs nges
NK047(tsi)006:11884: par 'jug spyir ni rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs legs
NK047(tsi)006:11885: par bzhengs la bkur sti bya rten 'brel bdag gi
NK047(tsi)006:11886: sku bzhengs nas bka' chems bsgrags la sems bskyed bya
NK047(tsi)006:11887: mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs la phyag 'tshal mchod
NK047(tsi)006:11888: bstod gsol 'debs na rnam dag tshul khrims legs par
NK047(tsi)006:11889: 'gyur rang gi snying gar gsal bsgoms pas byang chub
NK047(tsi)006:11890: sems mchog 'byongs par 'gyur dbyer med sku yi nga
NK047(tsi)006:11891: rgyal bzung dngos grub thob cing dge 'dun 'du zhes
NK047(tsi)006:11892: pa la sogs pa bzhin du dus mthar rgyal bstan
NK047(tsi)006:11893: la phan pa'i rten 'brel sogs dgos pa'i mchog du
NK047(tsi)006:11896: theg mchog khang bzangs yangs par zab gsal blo yi smin legs ma //
NK047(tsi)006:11897: gzhung mang rgyan gyis nyer mdzes lhag bsam zur mig g.yo bzhin du //
NK047(tsi)006:11898: bden gnyis rigs pa'i rgyud mngas rnam dpyod sor mos bsnun nas kyang /
NK047(tsi)006:11899: legs bshad mgrin pa'i glu dbyangs 'jam mgon dgyes pa'i ched du spel /
NK047(tsi)006:11900: kye ma bod gzhung tshig mang don chung tshegs che ji tsam sbyangs kyang the tshom rgya /
NK047(tsi)006:11901: bkrol la nus pa mi rno rnams la yun ring 'bad nas gzhung mchog 'di lta bu //
NK047(tsi)006:11902: spobs pa'i mchog sbyin yid gnyis gcod la 'jam dbyangs phyag gi ral gri ltar rno ba /
NK047(tsi)006:11903: gus pas mi 'dzin de dag skal pa ci zhig gyur snyam bdag ni yid skyo 'phel /
NK047(tsi)006:11904: de phyir rnyed dang grags pa'i blo med par //
NK047(tsi)006:11905: bla ma'i bka' dang lhag bsam bzang po dang //
NK047(tsi)006:11906: mchog dang mchog gi bstan la gus pa yis //
NK047(tsi)006:11907: rigs pa'i lam mchog rigs pa'i tshul gyis bkral //
NK047(tsi)006:11908: rgyal ba'i chos tshul nam mkha'i mtha' lta bu //
NK047(tsi)006:11909: slob pa'i 'phags rnams kyis kyang gzhal dka' na //
NK047(tsi)006:11910: byis pa'i blo can bdag gis smos ci 'tshal //
NK047(tsi)006:11911: de phyir nongs par gyur na mthol zhing bshags //
NK047(tsi)006:11912: lung bzang rin chen snang ba la brten nas //
NK047(tsi)006:11913: rigs pa'i 'dren byed gsal por bgrad byas pas //
NK047(tsi)006:11914: tshul lugs bzang po mthong nas gang sbyar ba'i //
NK047(tsi)006:11915: legs byas ston ka'i zla 'dra dri med des //
NK047(tsi)006:11916: so so yang dag rig pa bzhi yi sgo //
NK047(tsi)006:11917: rigs pa'i gzhung bzang zab mo 'di lta bu //
NK047(tsi)006:11918: rang gis rtogs nas gzhan la 'doms pa la //
NK047(tsi)006:11919: smra ba'i seng ge'i brtul zhugs 'grub gyur cig /
NK047(tsi)006:11920: gang gis gzhung 'di 'chad nyan klog pa yi //
NK047(tsi)006:11921: snying la 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i 'od zhugs nas //
NK047(tsi)006:11922: mkhan chen chos kyi rgyal po'i ring lugs gang //
NK047(tsi)006:11923: mi nyams phyogs dus kun tu spel gyur cig /
NK047(tsi)006:11924: grub mtha' kun gyi gnad gsang 'byin byed cing //
NK047(tsi)006:11925: phra zhing zab mo'i don kun rjen par ston //
NK047(tsi)006:11926: rigs lam 'di 'dra'i tshul dang gang gi blo //
NK047(tsi)006:11927: mtshungs par sbyor pa smra ba'i seng ge yin //
NK047(tsi)006:11928: gzhung bzang nor bu'i rgyan mchog 'di mthong na //
NK047(tsi)006:11929: rnam mang bstod pa'i 'ud ldan gzhan gyi gzhung //
NK047(tsi)006:11930: byis pa'i snyems pa spel byed mching bu'i rgyan //
NK047(tsi)006:11931: bzang por rloms pa'i zhe 'dod cis mi lhod //
NK047(tsi)006:11932: snying gi pad+mo rab tu bzhad par mkhan chen mchog dang 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK047(tsi)006:11933: dbyer med zhal gyi gzi byin bye bas rmongs pa'i mun pa mthar byas te //
NK047(tsi)006:11934: mkha' khyab 'gro la gcig tu brtse bas mkha' bzhin rtag tu srid pa 'dir //
NK047(tsi)006:11935: mkha' 'dra dri med zab mo'i chos kyi rgyal rnga mchog tu brdung gyur cig /
NK047(tsi)006:11936: mi bzad dus kyi snyigs ma nyi 'od nub pa'i smag bzhin ches cher 'khrigs na yang /
NK047(tsi)006:11937: rgyal dang rgyal sras thugs bskyed sprin med mkha' la zla ba bye ba ltar gsal nas //
NK047(tsi)006:11938: bka' dang bka' yi dgongs 'grel dri ma med rnams bshad dang sgrub pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK047(tsi)006:11939: bstan dang 'gro ba'i dge legs snang ba gong nas gong du 'phel zhing rgyas gyur cig /
NK047(tsi)006:11940: ces dbu ma rgyan gyi gzhung rnam par bshad pa
NK047(tsi)006:11941: 'adi'ang gong du ji skad smos pa lta bus mtshon
NK047(tsi)006:11942: te dgos pa'i dbang du ma gzigs nas /
NK047(tsi)006:11943: mkhan slob chos gsum gyi thugs rje gcig tu bsdus
NK047(tsi)006:11944: pa mkhas shing grub brnyes thams cad kyi rgyal po
NK047(tsi)006:11945: / mkhyen mchog zur phud lnga pa nyid ngur smrig
NK047(tsi)006:11946: 'dzin pa'i dge slong gi gzugs su rnam par rol
NK047(tsi)006:11947: / pa / bdag cag gi 'dren mchog mtshungs med
NK047(tsi)006:11948: tshad med pa'i bka' drin gyi mnga' bdag mtshan brjod
NK047(tsi)006:11949: / pa / par dka' ba / 'jam dbyangs mkhyen
NK047(tsi)006:11950: brtse'i dbang po zhes snyan pa'i ba dan srid par
NK047(tsi)006:11951: yongs su grags pa de nyid kyis /
NK047(tsi)006:11952: rgya bod kyi 'grel pa'i yig cha rnams gnang nas
NK047(tsi)006:11953: zhib tu ltos la 'grel bshad cig gyis zhes pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11954: rdo rje'i bka' lung spyi bor phebs pa gus pas
NK047(tsi)006:11956: shin tu phra ba'i gzhung lugs 'di lta bu la
NK047(tsi)006:11957: 'grel ba rtsom pa'i nus pa ni dman pa bdag
NK047(tsi)006:11959: rje btsun bla ma'i byin rlabs kyis cung zad 'dri ba'i spobs pa skyes pa'i tshe /
NK047(tsi)006:11960: snga 'gyur gyi ring lugs pa chen po pad+ma'i mtshan
NK047(tsi)006:11961: gyis kyang nan tan du bris shig pa'i gsung gnang
NK047(tsi)006:11962: bas kyang brtson pa bskyed de /
NK047(tsi)006:11963: rang lo so gcig pa rab tshes me byi'i bgrang
NK047(tsi)006:11964: bya gsar du shar ba'i nag pa zla ba'i tshes
NK047(tsi)006:11966: snga thun rnams su brgyud mar bris te zla ba
NK047(tsi)006:11967: de nyid kyi tshes nyer bzhi la rdzogs par bgyid
NK047(tsi)006:11968: pa po ni / rje mtshungs med mkhyen brtse'i dbang
NK047(tsi)006:11969: po de nyid kyi zhabs rdul la spyi bos reg
NK047(tsi)006:11970: pa'i mthu las blo gros kyi 'jug pa cung zad
NK047(tsi)006:11971: pa po ni / thob cing / gzhan yang nges
NK047(tsi)006:11972: pa don gyi rdo rje 'chang chen po dbang chen
NK047(tsi)006:11974: gnas lnga rig pa'i pan+di ta karma ngag dbang yon tan rgya mtsho dang /
NK047(tsi)006:11975: rgyal sras mkhas pa'i khyu mchog 'jigs med chos kyi
NK047(tsi)006:11976: dbang po sogs dam pa du ma'i bka' drin gyis
NK047(tsi)006:11977: bskyangs pas rgyal bstan la dad pa'i snang ba cung
NK047(tsi)006:11978: zad thob pa / rig byed kyi btags ming du
NK047(tsi)006:11979: 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rang mdangs mtsho byung bzhad pa'i
NK047(tsi)006:11980: ge sar du 'bod pa bdag gis bris shing /
NK047(tsi)006:11981: slar yang skyabs rje dam pa nyid las dag snang
NK047(tsi)006:11982: nye brgyud kyi bshad lung zab mo legs par nos
NK047(tsi)006:11983: nas / de ma thag sdom brtson sde snod 'dzin
NK047(tsi)006:11984: pa chen po bkra shis kyi grangs la zhag nyer
NK047(tsi)006:11985: gcig gi ring du bshad khrid bgyis pa'i skabs su
NK047(tsi)006:11986: cung zad zhus dag tu byas pa 'dis /
NK047(tsi)006:11987: rgyal ba nyi ma'i gnyen gyi ring lugs yang dag
NK047(tsi)006:11988: pa'i rigs lam seng ge'i sgra bo che 'jig rten
NK047(tsi)006:11989: gyi khams kun na rtag tu khyab par bsgrags pas
NK047(tsi)006:11992: kla klo la sogs pa pha rol gyi rgol ba'i
NK047(tsi)006:11993: spobs pa ma lus pa lhag med du bcom nas
NK047(tsi)006:11994: / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che phyogs
NK047(tsi)006:11995: dus kun na rgyal zhing rgyas pa'i rten 'byung du
NK047(tsi)006:11999: sras bcas rgyal ba'i mkhyen rab 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK047(tsi)006:12000: ngur smrig 'dzin pa'i gzugs su rnam rol pas //
NK047(tsi)006:12001: thub bstan chos kyi rgyal mtshan legs 'dzugs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:12002: mkhan chen chos kyi rgyal po rgyal gyur cig 1 /
NK047(tsi)006:12003: gang de'i rnam dpyod mtsho chen las 'ongs pa //
NK047(tsi)006:12004: legs bshad nyi ma brgya pa'i snang ba yis //
NK047(tsi)006:12005: srid pa'i smag rum gtan du zad byed pa'i //
NK047(tsi)006:12006: gzhung lugs rgyal bstan mdzes pa'i rgyan gcig gang /
NK047(tsi)006:12008: 2 / mkhas shing grub brnyes bye ba'i blo gros kyis //
NK047(tsi)006:12009: yang yang bzung byas rig lam seng ge'i sgra //
NK047(tsi)006:12010: rgyun mar bsgrags pas 'phags bod 'dzin ma'i khyon //
NK047(tsi)006:12011: kun dag'i dpal dang ldan par gyur mod kyi /
NK047(tsi)006:12013: 3 / dus kyi dbang gis 'chad dang nyan pa'i sgo //
NK047(tsi)006:12014: re zhig ngal bsos bzhin du gyur na yang //
NK047(tsi)006:12015: rigs gsum sems dpa'i rnam thar gcig bsdus pa //
NK047(tsi)006:12016: snyigs ma'i rgud pa kun sel bstan 'gro'i mgon /
NK047(tsi)006:12018: 4 / 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po zhes grags pa'i //
NK047(tsi)006:12019: snyan pa'i ba dan srid na mngon mtho ba //
NK047(tsi)006:12020: gang gi thugs bskyed zab mo'i byin rlabs dang //
NK047(tsi)006:12021: dgyes pa'i gsung gi snang ba la brten nas /
NK047(tsi)006:12023: 5 / mdo sngags bstan pa yongs su rdzogs pa yi //
NK047(tsi)006:12024: bshad dang sgrub pa'i lam srol dri med pa //
NK047(tsi)006:12025: sngon gyi dus bzhin slar yang gsal ba na //
NK047(tsi)006:12026: da gdod thub bstan bdud rtsi'i myong ba shes /
NK047(tsi)006:12028: 6 / theg mchog dbu ma chen po'i rigs pa'i gnad //
NK047(tsi)006:12029: gzhung bzang 'di 'dra'i tshul la brten nas su //
NK047(tsi)006:12030: the tshom smag dang bral bar nges byed pa'i //
NK047(tsi)006:12031: blo ldan blo yi snang ba 'phel bya'i phyir /
NK047(tsi)006:12033: 7 / zab mo dbu ma'i rgyan gyi gzhung nyid la //
NK047(tsi)006:12034: gsal zhing go bder bshad pa'i 'grel pa 'di'i //
NK047(tsi)006:12035: 'dzad med chos tshar sbar gyi bkod pa yang //
NK047(tsi)006:12036: mtshungs med dpal ldan bla ma'i phrin las lags /
NK047(tsi)006:12038: 8 / 'di yi dge bas sa gsum 'gro ba kun //
NK047(tsi)006:12039: zab cing rgya che'i shes rab gter grol nas //
NK047(tsi)006:12040: bde bar gshegs pa'i chos mdzod ma lus pa //
NK047(tsi)006:12041: 'chad nyan rtsom pas 'jig rten mdzes gyur cig 9 /
NK047(tsi)006:12042: thub bstan yongs su rdzogs pa'i lus stobs rgyas //
NK047(tsi)006:12043: rigs lam rno dbal 'khor lo'i sna zhags can //
NK047(tsi)006:12044: legs bshad 'chi med bzhon pa 'dir brten nas //
NK047(tsi)006:12045: rgyal bstan phyogs las rnam par rgyal gyur cig 10 /
NK047(tsi)006:12046: ces pa'ang spar byang smon tshig bcas rje bla ma'i
NK047(tsi)006:12047: bka' yi snang bas skyong ba 'jam dpal dgyes pas
